var book = {
	"name": "Markos",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kaba sdang ka gospel U Jisu Khrist, U Khun U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kat kumba la thoh ha ki nongïathuhlypa, “Ha khmih, nga phah ïa u nongbuhai jong nga ha shuwa ka khmat jong me, u ban khreh ïa ka lynti jong me.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka ktien jong uba pyrta ha ka ri khlaw, ‘Phin pynkhreh ïa ka lynti bah U Trai, phin pynbeit ruh ïa ki lynti jong u.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Ïoannis u la pynbaptis ha ka ri khlaw, bad u la ïalap ïa ka jingbaptis ka jingkylla-ka-bamut ïa ka ban map ki pop.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hangta te kiba na ka ri Judia, bad ki Jerusalem baroh ki la leit ha u, bad la pynbaptis ïa ki da u ha ka wah Jordan, ki da ïaphla noh ïa ki pop jong ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Ïoannis u la kup da ka jaiñ shñiuh ut, bad ka jingpanpoh snieh ha ka syngkai jong u, bad u la bam da ki puit bad ka ngap khlaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la ïalap ruh, u da ong, “Don uba wan nadien jong nga uba kham khraw bor ïa nga, kam dei ïa nga ban dem ïa ka ban loit wat tang ïa ki jingteh ki juti jong u:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> nga shisha nga la pynbaptis ïa phi da ka um; hynrei, uta un pynbaptis ïa phi da U Mynsiem Bakhuid.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kita ki sngi, ba U Jisu u la wan na Nasaret kaba ha Galilaïa, bad la pynbaptis ïa u da u Ïoannis ha ka Jordan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh haba u dang kiew noh na ka um, u la ïohi ba la plie ïa ki bneng, bad U Mynsiem u hiar ha u kum ka paro.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka ktien te ka la wan na bneng, ka da ong, “Me long U Khun jong nga uba ieit, ha me nga sngewbha eh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, U Mynsiem u la ïalam noh kyrkieh ïa u sha ka ri khlaw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la don te ha kata ka ri khlaw sawphew sngi, ba la pynshoi ïa u da u Soitan; bad u la don ryngkat bad ki mrad khlaw, bad ki angel ki la ïashakri ïa u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te hadien ba la byndi ïa u Ïoannis, U Jisu u la wan sha Galilaïa, u da ïalap ïa ka gospel U Blei,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u da ong ruh, “La pyndep ïa ka Ïa, bad ka hima U Blei ka la jan: to phin kylla-ka-bamut, bad to ngeit ruh ïa ka gospel.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u dang ïaid harud ka duriaw Galilaïa, u la ïohi ïa u Simon bad ïa u Andriw u para jong u, ba ki dang ïabred ïa ka jar ha duriaw; naba ki long ki nongtong dohkha.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “To wan bud nadien jong nga, te ngan pynlong ïa phi ki nongtong briew.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kumta, ki la iehnoh dak ïa ki jar jong ki, bad ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Haba u la nang leit nangta ruh kham jngai khyndiat, u la ïohi ïa u Jakob u khun u Sebedi, bad u Ïoannis u para jong u, kiba don de ha ka lieng ba ki dang shna ïa ki jar.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumne kumne ruh, u la khot ïa ki; ki ruh, haba ki la iehnoh ïa u Sebedi u kpa jong ki ha kata la lieng lem bad ki nongbylla, ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki la rung ruh sha Kapernam: te kumne kumne ruh, ha ka sngi Sabbaton u la rung sha ka synagog, bad u la hikai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki la sngewkyndit te ïa ka jinghikai jong u, naba u la hikai ïa ki kum uba don bor, ym kum ki nongthoh keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te la don ha ka synagog jong ki, u briew uba don u mynsiem bymkhuid: bad u la pyrta,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u da ong, “Iehnoh ïa ngi; me donkam aïu bad ngi, me U Jisu uba na Nasaret? me la wan khnang ban pynjot ïa ngi? nga ithuh ïa me uei me long, U Bakhuid u jong U Blei.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Jisu te u la dumok ïa u, U da ong, “Wat jam me, to mih noh ruh na u.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Uta u mynsiem bymkhuid te, da kaba ring kyrthat ïa u bad da kaba pyrta da ka ktien bajam, u la mih noh na u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Baroh te ki la sngewkyndit, kat ban ïakylli hi paralok, ki da ong, “Kaei kane? ka jinghikai bathymmai! da ka bor U hukum wat kat ïa ki mynsiem bymkhuid, ki ruh ki kohnguh ïa U!”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te shen shen ruh, ka jingbna shaphang jong U ka la phriang kylleng sawdong kata ka ri Galilaïa baroh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, haba ki la mih noh na kata ka synagog, ki la rung sha ka ïing u Simon bad u Andriw, lem bad u Jakob bad u Ïoannis ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, ka syngken kurim u Simon ka thiah ba ka khieshoh; te kumta kumta ki ïathuh ha U shaphang jong ka.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te U la wan bad U la bat ïa ka na ka kti, bad U la khyllie ïa ka; te kata ka khieshoh ka la iehnoh ïa ka, bad ka la shakri ïa ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ynda la janmiet te, haba la sep ka sngi, ki la wallam ha u ïa ki bapang baroh, bad ïa kita kiba shong ksuid ruh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te baroh shi shnong ki la ïawan lang ha ka jingkhang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la pynkhiah shibun kiba la pang na ki jingpang babun jaid, bad u la beh noh shibun ki ksuid; bad um shah ïa kita ki ksuid ban kren, namar ba ki ithuh ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ha kaba lashai mynstep, dang slem eh ban mih ka sngi, haba u la khie u la mih noh, bad u la leit noh sha ka jaka kynjah, bad hangta u la duwai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Simon bad kita kiba don lem bad u, ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad haba ki la shem ïa U, ki la ong ha U, “Baroh ki ïawad ïa me.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ïa ngin ïaleit shawei pat sha ki shnong kiba marjan, ba ngan ïoh ïalap hangta ruh; naba ïa kata keiñ, nga la mih noh.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U la ïalap te ha ki synagog jong ki kylleng sawdong ka Galilaïa baroh, u la beh noh de ïa ki ksuid.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh u la wan ha U, u da kyrpad ïa U, bad u da dem khohsiew ha U, bad u da ong ha U, “Lada me mon, me lah ban pynkhuid ïa nga.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te U Jisu haba U la sngewsynei, U la kner ïa la ka kti bad U la ktah ïa u, bad U ong ha u, “Nga mon; to men long khuid.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te U tang shu la kren, uta u 'ñiangthohlieh u la iehnoh ïa u, bad la pynkhuid ïa u.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te haba U la hukum skhem ïa u, U la phah noh kumne kumne ruh;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad U la ong ha u, “Sumar men ym ïathuh ei ei hano hano; hynrei, khie leit noh, pyni ïa lade ha u lyngdoh, bad to ainguh na ka bynta ka jingkhuid jong me ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba u Moses u la hukum, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ïa ki.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hynrei, haba u la mih noh, u la sdang ban pynbna haw, bad ban pynphriang kylleng ïa kata ka ktien, katba U Jisu um lah leit shuh shapoh kata ka shnong ha kaba paw; hynrei, U la shong shabar ha ki jaka kynjah, bad ki la wan ha U na baroh sawdong."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda U la leit pat shapoh Kapernam hadien khyndiat sngi, la pynbna ba U don ha ïing.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te bun ki la ïalang, katba ym ngiam jaka shuh, em, wat haduh ka jingkhang: bad u la ïalap ïa ka ktien ha ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki wan ruh ha U kiba wallam ïa uwei u bapang ïapshiliang, ïa uba ki bah saw ngut.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda kim lah wan hajan jong U namar uta u paidbah, ki la ïalied noh ïa ka jingsop na ka jaka ha kaba U la don, bad haba ki la pynpei, ki la ïa-pynhiar noh ïa ka jingthiah ha kaba u la thiah uta u bapang ïapshiliang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba U Jisu u la ïohi ïa ka jingngeit jong ki, U la ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang, “Ko khun, la map noh ïa me ïa ki pop jong me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, don kiba na ki nongthoh kiba shong hangta, bad kiba ïapyrkhat ha la ki dohnud,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Balei ba une u kren kaba beiñ blei kumne? uei uba lah ban map ïa ki pop, hynrei, tang U Blei hi?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, haba U Jisu u la tip ha la ka mynsiem, ba ki la ïapyrkhat kumta ha lade, U la ong ha ki, “Balei ba phi ïapuson ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ha la ki dohnud?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> kano kaba kham jem, ban ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang, ‘La map ïa ki pop jong me’; ne ban ong, ‘To ïeng, to rah noh ïa la ka jingthiah, to ïaid ruh?’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynrei, ba phin ïoh tip ba U Khun u briew u don bor ha ka khyndew ban map ïa ki pop”, (U ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang),",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Ha me nga ong, To ïeng joit, rah noh ïa la ka jingthiah, bad leit noh sha la ïing.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, u la ïeng, bad u la rah noh ïa kata ka jingthiah, u la mih noh de ha khmat jong ki baroh; katba ki la kyndit noh baroh, bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Blei, ki da ong, “Mynno mynno ruh ngim ju ïohi kat kane!”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la leit noh pat ruh harud ka duriaw: te u paidbah baroh u la wan ha U, bad U la hikai ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te katba U nang ïaid noh nangta, U la ïohi ïa u Lebi u khun u Alphaïos ba u shong ha ïing khrong, U la ong te ha u, “To bud ïa nga.” Te u la ïeng bad u la bud ïa U.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U la shong bam ha ïing jong u, ba shibun ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop ki la shong lem bad U Jisu bad ki synran jong U: naba ki la long shibun, bad ki la ïabud ïa U.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi ki la ïohi ïa U ba U ïabam lem bad kita ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop, ki la ong ha ki synran jong U, “U ïabam U ïadih ruh pleng bad ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop ruh.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew, U la ong ha ki, “Ki bakhiah kim donkam ïa u nongpynkhiah, hynrei, ki bapang keiñ: ngam shym la wan ban khot ïa ki bahok, hynrei, ïa ki bapop ïa ka ban kylla-ka-bamut.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki synran u Ïoannis bad ki jong ki Pharisi ki ïashah jingit: ki la wan te, bad ki la ong ha U, “Balei ba ki synran u Ïoannis bad ki jong ki Pharisi ki shah jingit, hynrei, ki synran jong me kim ïashah jingit?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “Ki nong-on kurim ki lah ban shah jingit, haba u nongleit-kurim u dang sah lem bad ki? katba ki dang don uta u nongleit-kurim lem bad ki, kim lah ban shah jingit:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, ki sngi kin poi, haba la shim noh ïa u nongleit-kurim na ki, ynda kumta te, ha kita ki sngi keiñ, kin sa ïashah jingit.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ym ju don ruh uba suh syrdep ïa ka jaiñkup barim da ka jaiñ thymmai: lada kumta, kata ka jaiñsyrdep bathymmai jong ka kan pynkad ïa ka barim, bad ka pynlong ka jingkad kaba kham khraw.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ym ju don ruh uba buh ïa ka Waiñ thymmai ha ki lywa snieh barim: lada kumta, kata ka Waiñ bathymmai kan pynpdang ïa ki lywa snieh, bad kata ka Waiñ ka jaw noh bad kita ki lywa snieh ki jot noh: hynrei ïa ka Waiñ thymmai ju buh ha ki lywa snieh thymmai.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ka la jia ba U la ïaid lyngba ïa ki lyngkha Kew ha ka sngi Sabbaton; bad ki synran jong U, katba ki ïaid, ki la sdang kheit soh Kew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki Pharisi te ki la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, balei ba ki leh ïa ka bymdei ha ka sngi Sabbaton?”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Mynno mynno ruh phim pat ju pule ïa kaei ba u Dabid u la leh, mynba u la shipa, bad ba u la thngan, ma u, bad kita kiba bad u ruh?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumno ba u la leit hapoh ka ïing U Blei ha ki sngi u Abiathar u rangbah lyngdoh, bad ba u la bam ïa ki 'pu pyni, ïa ki bymbit ban bam, hynrei, tang ïa ki lyngdoh hi, bad ba u la ai ruh de ha kita kiba don lem bad u?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u la ong ruh ha ki, “La thaw ïa ka Sabbaton na ka bynta u briew, ym ïa u briew na ka bynta ka Sabbaton:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ba kumta te U Khun u briew u long U Trai ka Sabbaton ruh.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U la leit pat hapoh ka synagog; bad la don hangta u briew uba la ïap ka kti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki la ïa-ap thap ïa U, lada un pynkhiah ïa u ha ka sngi Sabbaton; ba kin ïoh kem daw ïa U.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U ong te ha uta u briew uba la ïap ka kti, “To ïeng hapdeng.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te U ong ha ki, “Ka bit ïa ka ban leh bha ha ka sngi Sabbaton, lane ban leh sniew? ïa ka ban pynim ïa ka jingim, lane ban pynïap?” Hynrei, ki la sngap jar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda U la khmih sawdong ha ki da ka jingbitar, ba U da sngewsih namar kaba eh ka dohnud jong ki, U ong ha uta u briew, “To kner noh ïa la ka kti.” Te u la kner noh, bad la pynkhiah bha ïa kata ka kti jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba ki Pharisi te ki la leit noh, kumne kumne ruh, ki la ïasylla bad ki nongbud u Herod pyrshah ïa U, kumno ba kin ïoh pynïap noh ïa U.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei U Jisu u la kynriah noh lem bad la ki synran sha ka duriaw, te ki paidbah byllien ki la ïabud ïa u na Galilaïa, bad na Judia,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad na Jerusalem, bad na Idumia, bad na sha shiliang ka Jordan ruh; bad kiba na shaphang Tyros bad Sidon, u paidbah byllien kiba haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kaba katno u la leh, ki la ïawan ha u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U la ong te ha ki synran jong u, ba ka lieng rit kan ap hajan jong u, namar uta u paidbah, ïoh ba kin kyntur ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar u la lah pynkhiah shibun, katba kita baroh kiba la ngat ki jingpang kordit ki la wan kyrthep ha u ba kin ïoh ktah ïa u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki mynsiem bymkhuid ruh, haba ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la dem khrup ha khmat jong u, bad ki la ïapyrta, ki da ong, “Me long U Khun U Blei!”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la hukum skhem ïa ki, ba kin ym pynbna ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u kiew sha u lum, bad u khot ha u ïa kiba u mon hi, te ki la wan ha u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la thung ïa ki khat-ar ngut, ba kin ïoh long lem bad u, bad ba un ïoh phah ïa ki ban ïalap,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ba kin ïoh bor ban pynkhiah ïa ki jingpang bad ban beh noh ïa ki ksuid,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ïa u Simon u la sin “Petros”;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u Jakob u khun u Sebedi, bad u Ïoannis u para u Jakob (te ïa kita u la sin “Boanerjes”, kata ka long, “Ki khun u pyrthat”);",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u Andriw, bad u Philip, bad u Bartholomai, bad u Mathaïos, bad u Thomas, bad u Jakob u khun u Alphaïos, bad u Thaddaïos, bad u Simon u Bashitrhem,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u Judas Iskariot, uba la die noh ruh ïa U.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la wan sha ïing. U paidbah te u la wan lang pat, katba kim ïoh shuh wat ïa ka ban bam jingbam.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba ki kur jong u ki la bna, ki la leit noh ban bat ïa u, naba ki la ong, “Um tipbriew shuh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki nongthoh kiba la wan hiar na Jerusalem ki la ong, “U don u Belsebul, bad da u rangbah ki ksuid U beh noh ïa ki ksuid.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u la khot ïa ki ha u, u la kren ïa ki ha ki pharshi. “Kumno u Soitan u lah ban shop noh ïa u Soitan?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad lada ka hima ka la ïaleh makynti paralok, kata ka hima kam lah neh shuh:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad lada ka ïing de ka la ïaleh makynti paralok, kata ka ïing kam lah neh shuh:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad lada u Soitan de u ïeng ban ïaleh hi ïa lade, bad u la ïapait, um lah neh shuh, hynrei, don keiñ ka bakut ïa u:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ym don uno uno ruh uba leit hapoh ka ïing u bakhlaiñ, uba lah ban kurup ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong u, lymda u khum shuwa ïa uta u bakhlaiñ; ynda kumta te, un sa kurup ïa ka ïing jong u:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba yn map ïa ki khun bynriew ïa ki pop baroh, bad ïa ki jingkrenbeiñ blei katba kin krenbeiñ blei,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban krenbeiñ ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ha la ka rta un ym ïoh ka jingmap, hynrei, u ban rem na ka pop bymjukut.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba ki la ong, “U don mynsiem bymkhuid.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Haba kumta te, ki hynmen hynbew jong u bad ka kmie jong u ruh ki la wan; bad haba ki la ïeng shabar, ki la phah ha u, ba ki da khot noh ïa u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u paidbah u la shong tawiar ïa u, bad ki la ong ha u, “Ha khmih ka kmie jong me bad ki hynmen hynbew jong me habar ki ïawad ïa me.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U la ïathuh te ha ki, u da ong, “Kano ka kmie jong nga, lane ki hynmen hynbew jong nga?”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba u la khmih baroh sawdong ïa kiba shong tawiar ïa u, u ong, “Ha khmih ka kmie jong nga, bad ki hynmen hynbew jong nga!",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> naba uno uno ruh u ban leh ïa ka mon U Blei, uta keiñ, u long u para jong nga bad ka para jong nga, bad ka kmie de.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U la sdang ruh ban hikai pat harud ka duriaw: te u paidbah byllien u la wan lang ha U, katba U la kiew ha ka lieng ban ïoh shong halor ka duriaw; uta u paidbah baroh te u la don harud kata ka duriaw ha ryngkew.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U la hikai ïa ki, bun kiei kiei ruh ha ki pharshi, bad U la ong ha ki ha ka jinghikai jong U,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “To sngew: Ha khmih, u nongbet u la leit noh ban bet:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te ka la jia haba u dang bet, ba don uba la hap harud lynti, bad ki sim bneng ki la wan bad ki la bam ïa u:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> te uwei pat u la hap halor ka jaka maw, ha ka bymdon bun khyndew; te kumne kumne ruh, u la mih, naba kam long jylliew ka khyndew:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> haba ka la ïeng ka sngi, te u la shit tyrkhong eh; bad naba um don thied, u la ïap ryngkhiang:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> uwei pat te u la hap hapdeng ki dieng shiah; te kita ki dieng shiah ki la ïamih, bad ki la ïakjap ïa u; te um shym la sei soh:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> uwei pat te u la hap ha ka khyndew ka babha, bad u la sei soh ba mih bad ba man bun de; te u la sei uba laiphew shah, bad uba hynriewphew shah, bad uba shispah shah.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Haba u la long te kyrpang weibriew, kita kiba hajan jong u lem bad kita ki khat-ar ngut, ki la kylli ïa u shaphang kata ka pharshi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ha phi keiñ, la ai ban tip ïa ka maïan ka hima U Blei: hynrei, ha kita kiba shabar, ïa kiei kiei baroh yn leh keiñ, ha ki pharshi:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “ ‘Ba ïa kaba ki ïohi kin ïohi, te kin ym ishemphang shuh; bad ïa kaba ki ïohsngew kin ïohsngew, te kin ym sngewthuh shuh; ba ïoh kumta kin kylla, bad yn map ïa ki.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Phim tip ïa kane ka pharshi? kumno te phin tip ïa ki pharshi baroh?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uta u nongbet u bet ïa ka ktien:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kine te long kita kiba harud lynti, ha kaba la bet ïa ka ktien; hynrei, haba ki la ïohsngew, kumne kumne ruh u Soitan u wan, bad u rong noh ïa kata ka ktien ba la bet ha ki dohnud jong ki:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> kumjuh ruh kine ki long kita kiba la bet halor ka jaka maw, kiba, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien, kumne kumne ruh ki pdiang ïa ka da kaba kmen;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> hynrei, ba kim don thied ha lade, ki long tang shibit; hadien te, haba ka jia kaba jynjar ne kaba lehbeiñ na ka bynta kata ka ktien, kumne kumne ruh, ki la thut:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kine ruh ki long kita kiba la bet hapdeng ki dieng shiah; kiba ju sngew ïa ka ktien,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te ki jingkhuslai kane ka pyrthei, bad ka jingshukor ka spah, bad ki jingikwah eh shaphang kiwei kiwei de, haba ki ïaleit hapoh, ki ïakjap ïa kata ka ktien, te kam sei soh shuh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kine te ki long kita kiba la bet ha ka khyndew ka babha; kiba ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien, bad kiba pdiang ïa ka, bad kiba sei soh, uba laiphew shah, bad uba hynriewphew shah, bad uba shispah shah de.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Ki ju wallam ïa ka sharak, ba yn buh hapoh ka shang, lane hapoh ka jingthiah? bad ban ym buh ha ka dieng pynïeng sharak?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> naba ym don kaei kaei ruh ba la tap, ïa kaba yn ym pynpaw; lymne ym ju don kaei kaei ruh ba la buhrieh, hynrei, khnang ba kan wan paw:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> lada uno uno ruh u don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “To sumar kumno ba phi sngew: da ka jingthew ba phi thew, yn thew ïa phi; ha phi kiba sngew, yn ai kham bun ruh;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> naba jar uba don, ha uta yn ai: bad jar u bymdon, wat ïa kata kaba u don yn shim noh na u.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U la ong ruh, “Kumta long ka hima U Blei, kumba u briew un bet ïa u symbai ha ka khyndew,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ba un ïohthiah, bad ba un khie ruh mynmiet bad mynsngi, bad uta u symbai un mih, bad un nang san, kumno, u um tip shuh:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> naba ka khyndew na lade hi ka sei soh; ka banyngkong u speh, hadien ka kop, hadien kata pat, u soh Kew ba la met ha ka kop:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> hynrei, haba la ih uta u soh, kumne kumne ruh u sei ïa ka rashi, naba ka aïom ot ka la poi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U la ong ruh, “Kum kaei ngin ïatharai ïa ka hima U Blei? ne da kano ka pharshi ngin ïatharai ïa ka?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ka long kum u symbai tyrso, ïa uba, haba la bet ha ka khyndew, la u long kham rit ïa ki symbai baroh kiba don ha ka khyndew;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> hynrei, haba la bet, u mih u san, bad u long kham khraw ïa ki jhur baroh, bad u sei ïa ki tnat bakhraw, katba ki sim bneng ki lah ban shongtngen hapoh ka syrngiew jong u.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Da ki bun ki pharshi ruh kum kine u la kren ïa ka ktien ha ki, katba ki lah ban sngew-shemphang ïa ka.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad khlem ka pharshi, um shym la kren ha ki: te haba kyrpang hi u la ju pynpaw ïa kiei kiei baroh ha ki synran jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki ha kata ka sngi, haba la janmiet, “Ïa ngin ïaleit sha shiliang.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Haba ki la iehnoh te ïa u paidbah, ki la leit lam ïa U kumba U long, ha ka lieng; hynrei, don kiwei pat ruh ki lieng lem bad U.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te la khih ka 'erïong ka bakhraw, bad ki jingat phyllung ki la phaloh sha ka lieng, kat ban sa pyndap ïa ka.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U te u la don ha ka tdong ka lieng, ba u ïohthiah ha ka syngkhlieh; ki te ki kyrsiew ïa u, bad ki ong ha u, “Ko Kynrad, mem suidñiew satia ba ngin sa ïap?”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Haba u la khie te, u la sneng ïa ka lyer, bad u la ong ha ka duriaw, “Long jai jai, wat khih shuh.” Kumta, kata ka lyer ka la jem jai, bad ka la long kaba jai jai eh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Balei phi long kiba sheptieng katta katta? kumno ba phim pat don ka jingngeit?”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, ki la sheptieng shikatdei eh, bad ki la ïakren paralok hi, “Une u long uei shisha, ba ka lyer ruh bad ka duriaw de ki ïakohnguh ïa u?”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ki la poi ruh sha shiliang ka duriaw sha ka ri ki nong Gadara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba U la mih noh te na kata ka lieng, kumne kumne ruh, la wan tan ïa U na ki maw jingtep u briew bashong mynsiem bymkhuid,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> uba ju don ka jaka shong sah hapdeng kita ki maw jingtep; te ym don mano mano ruh ba lah ban khum ïa u, em, wat da ki kynjri;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> naba la ju khum jyndei ïa u da ki narkjat, bad da ki kynjri; hynrei, ïa ki kynjri u la ju bthat, bad ïa ki narkjat u la ju pynbthat lyngkhot lyngkhot: bad ym ju don mano mano ruh ba lah ban pynjuh ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te khlem da pud, mynmiet bad mynsngi, u ju don ha kita ki maw jingtep bad ha ki lum ruh, u da lynñiar, bad u da ot ïa lade da ki maw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba u la ïohi te ïa U Jisu na jngai, u la phet bad u la mane dem ïa U,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u la lynñiar da ka ktien bajam bad u la ong, “Me donkam aïu bad nga, ko Jisu, U Khun U Blei U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh? Nga pynsmai ïa me da U Blei, ba men ym pynshitom ïa nga.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> (Naba U la lah ong ha u, “Me mynsiem bymkhuid, to mih noh na une u briew.”)",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U la kylli ïa u, “Kaei ka kyrteng jong me?” U te u la ïathuh, u da ong, “Ka kyrteng jong nga long ‘U Paidbah’: naba ngi long shibun.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la kyrpad ruh ïa U shikatdei, ba un ym phah noh ïa ki na kata ka ri.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la don hangta ha syndah u lum, shi kynhun bah ki sniang kiba bam phlang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kita ki ksuid baroh te ki la ïakyrpad ïa U, ki da ong, “To phah ïa ngi ha kito ki sniang, ba ngin rung hapoh jong ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Jisu u la shah ïa ki. Haba la mih noh te kita ki mynsiem bymkhuid, ki la leit hapoh kita ki sniang: baroh shi kynhun, te ki la phet ïap arsut ïa ka riat sha ka duriaw (ki la don ruh kumba ar hajar), bad ki la ïap jyllop ha kata ka duriaw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kita kiba ïa-ap ïa ki sniang, te ki la phet noh, bad ki la ïathuh ha kata ka shnong bad ha kita ki ri bri: ki, te ki la ïamih ban khmih kaei kata ba la leh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki wan ha U Jisu, bad ki ïohi ïa uta uba ju shong ksuid ba u shong, bad ba u la kup jaiñ, bad ba u la tipbriew, ïa uta keiñ uba la ju don “u Paidbah”: bad ki la sheptieng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kita kiba la lah ïohi, te ki la ïathuh ha ki kumno ka la long ïa uta uba ju shong ksuid, bad shaphang kita ki sniang ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la sdang ban ïakyrpad ïa U ban leit noh na ki phang jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Haba U dang leit te ha kata ka lieng, uta uba la ju shong ksuid u la duwai ïa U ba un ïoh long lem bad U.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te um shah ïa u, hynrei, U ong ha u, “Khie leit sha la ïing sha la ki jong ruh, bad to ïathuh ha ki, ïa kaba katno ba U Trai u la leh ïa me, bad kumno u la isynei ïa me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, u la leit noh, bad u la sdang ban pynbna ha Dekapolis ïa kiba katno kiei kiei ruh ba U Jisu u la leh ha u; te baroh ki la kyndit.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la leit pat da ka lieng sha shiliang, u paidbah byllien u la ïalum lang ha U: U te U don harud ka duriaw.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te uwei na ki rangbah synagog u wan, uba kyrteng “u Jairos”; bad haba u ïohi ïa U, u la dem ha ki kjat jong U;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u la duwai shikatdei ïa U, u da ong, “Ka khun rit jong nga ka ha tmier ka jingïap: to wan buh ïa la ki kti ha ka, ban ïoh pynkhiah ïa ka, ba kan im.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, U la leit lem bad u: te la bud ïa U, u paidbah byllien, bad ki la ïakyntur ïa U.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka kynthei ruh kawei kaba don ka jingpang mihsnam la khat-ar snem,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad kaba la lah shah shitom bun kiei kiei ruh na ki bun ki nongpynkhiah, bad kaba la lah pynlut baroh katba don ki jong ka, te khyndiat ruh em kam shym koit, hynrei, ka la nang pang pynban;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> haba ka la ïohsngew shaphang U Jisu, ka la wan hapdeng uta u paidbah na shadien, bad ka la ktah ïa ka jaiñkup jong U.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Naba ka la ong, “Lada ngan shu ïoh ktah tang ïa ki jaiñkup jong U, ngan sa khiah.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, kata ka jingkyrsoi ka snam jong ka, ka la rngad noh; bad ka la sngewthuh ha la ka met ba ka la ïoh khiah na kata ka jingpang shitom.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Jisu kumne kumne ruh, ba U tip ha lade ba kata ka bor ka la lah mih noh na U, haba U la phai hapdeng uta u paidbah, U la ong, “Ei ba ktah ïa ki jaiñ jong nga?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki synran jong U te ki la ong ha U, “Me ïohi ïa u paidbah uba kyntur ïa me, me ong ruh, ‘Ktah mano ïa nga?’ ”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te U la khmih baroh sawdong ban ïohi ïa kata kaba la lah leh ïa kane.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, kata ka briew, da kaba sheptieng bad ba khynñiuh, ba ka da sngewthuh ïa kaei ba la leh ha ka, ka la wan bad ka la dem ngon ha khmat jong U, bad ka la ïathuh ha U ïa kaba shisha baroh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “Ko khun, ka jingngeit jong pha ka la pynkhiah ïa pha; to khie leit ha kaba suk, bad to long kaba la khiah bha na ka jingpang shitom jong pha.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Haba U dang kren, la wan kiba na ka ïing uta u rangbah synagog, ki da ong, “Ka khun jong me ka la ïap; balei men pynshitom shuh ïa U Nonghikai?”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien ba la kren, U ong ha uta u rangbah synagog, “Wat sheptieng, tang shu ngeit.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Um shah te ïano ïano ruh ban bud lem ïa U, hynrei, tang ïa u Petros, bad ïa u Jakob, bad ïa u Ïoannis u para u Jakob.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kumta, U poi sha ka ïing uta u rangbah synagog, bad U ïohi ïa ka jingkhihwin, bad ïa kiba ïambriew bad ïa kiba lynñiar shikatdei eh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Haba U la leit hapoh te, U ong ha ki, “Balei phi ïawin, bad phi ïaïambriew kumne? ka khynnah kam shym la ïap, hynrei, ka shu thiah.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ki te ki la rkhiebeiñ ïa U. Hynrei, haba U la pynmih noh ïa ki baroh, U shim lem ïa u kpa bad ïa ka kmie jong kata ka khynnah, bad ïa kita kiba don lem bad U, bad U la leit hapoh, sha kaba don kata ka khynnah.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te haba U la bat na ka kti ïa kata ka khynnah, U ong ha ka, “Talitha kumi;” kaba, haba la batai, ka long, “Ko khynnah, nga ong ha pha, to ïeng”.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kumne kumne ruh, kata ka khynnah ka la ïeng joit, bad ka la ïaid (naba ka la khat-ar snem ka rta); te ki la kyndit da ka jingkyndit bakhraw.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te U la hukum skhem ïa ki, ba uno uno ruh un ym tip ïa kane: U la hukum ruh ban ai ei ei ïa ka, ban bam."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U la leit noh nangta bad u la wan poi sha la ka ri: bad ki synran jong u ki bud ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba la poi ka Sabbaton, u la sdang ban hikai ha ka synagog: te bun haba ki ïohsngew ki la sngewkyndit, ki da ong, “Nangno une u la ïoh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh?” bad “Kaba kumno kane ka jingstad kaba la ai ha une u briew, bad ki kambah kat kine ba la leh da ki kti jong u?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> une um long uto u misteri, u khun ka Mari, uba dei para bad u Jakob, bad u Josis, bad u Juda, bad u Simon de? bad ki para kynthei jong u kim don hangne bad ngi?” Kumta, ki la thut ha u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “U nongïathuhlypa um long u bym donburom, hynrei, tang ha la ka ri, bad ha la ki kur, bad ha la ïing ruh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hangta te um lah ban leh ïa ki kambah, hynrei, u shu buh ïa la ki kti ha khyndiat ki bapang, bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la sngewkyndit te namar ka jingbymngeit jong ki. Bad u la ïaid kylleng sawdong ïa ki nongrit, u da hikai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la khot ruh ha u ïa ki khat-ar ngut, bad u la sdang ban phah ïa ki ar ar; bad u la ai bor ha ki halor ki mynsiem bymkhuid;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u la hukum ïa ki, ba kin ym rah ei ei ruh ïa la ka jingleit, hynrei, tang ïa u diengduh hi; lymne ki ïarong, lymne kpu, lymne pisa ha ka 'saipan jong ki,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hynrei, ban ïuh ïa ki khulom, bad ban ym phong ar tylli ki sopti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Ha-ei ha-ei ruh haba phin rung hapoh ka ïing, to shong hangta tad ynda phi mih noh nangta;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> te ha kano kano ruh ka jaka ka ban ym pdiang ïa phi, bad kim sngew ïa phi, haba phi mih noh nangta, to kynther noh ïa ka 'dewmet na ki poh'jat jong phi, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ïa ki. Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kan long kham jem ïa ka Sodom bad ïa ka Gomorra ha ka sngi bishar, ban ïa kaba ïa kata ka shnong.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ki la leit noh, ki la ïalap ba kin kylla-ka-bamut.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki la beh noh ruh shibun ki ksuid, bad ki la pynsleh da ka umphniang shibun ki bapang, bad ki la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Herod syiem te u la ïohsngew shaphang jong U, naba la bna ka nam jong U, bad u la ong, “U Ïoannis uba ju pynbaptis, u la mihpat na ki baïap, te namar kata keiñ, kine ki borbah ki ïatrei ha u.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kiwei te ki la ong, “U long u Elias”, kiwei pat te ki la ong, “U long u nongïathuhlypa”, ne kum uwei na ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, haba u Herod u la ïohsngew, u la ong, “U Ïoannis, ïa uba nga la khrai khlieh, u la mihpat.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba u Herod hi u la lah phah kem ïa u Ïoannis, bad u la lah khum ïa u ha ka byndi na ka bynta ka Herodias, ka tnga u Philip u para jong u; naba u la shongkurim ïa ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba u Ïoannis u la ong ha u Herod, “Bymbit ïa me ban ïoh ïa ka tnga u para jong me.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata, ka Herodias ka la buhnud ïa u, bad ka la kwah ban pynïap ïa u, hynrei, kam lah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba u Herod u la ju sheptieng ïa u Ïoannis, ba u da tip ba u long u briew bahok bad bakhuid, u la ju da te ïa u; bad haba u la ïohsngew ïa u, u la ju leh shibun kiei kiei ruh, bad u la ju shahshkor sngewbha ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, haba la poi ka sngi ba dei, mynba u Herod ha ka sngi kha jong u, u la thaw ka jingkhawai ïa ki rangbah jong u, bad ïa ki rangbah shihajar, bad ïa kiba kham donnam ha Galilaïa;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad haba ka khun kata ka Herodias ka la wan hapoh, ka la shad, bad ka la pynsngewbha ruh ïa u Herod, bad ïa kita kiba ïashong bam lem bad u; bad uta u syiem u la ong ha kata ka khynnah, “Pan na nga kat kaba pha mon, te ngan ai ïa pha.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U la smai ruh ha ka, “Kaei kaei ruh ba phan pan na nga, ngan ai ïa pha, haduh shiteng ka hima jong nga.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ka la mih noh, ka la ong ha ka kmie jong ka, “Kaei ngan pan?” Ka te ka la ong, “Ka khlieh u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te kloi lan ka la wan hapoh sha uta u syiem, bad ka la pan, ka da ong, “Nga mon ba men ai ha nga kumne kumne ïa ka khlieh u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis ha ka pliang.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Uta u syiem te u la sngewsih eh, hynrei, na ka bynta kita ki jingsmai, bad na ka bynta kita kiba ïashong bam lem bad u, um mon ban kyrngah ïa ka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh uta u syiem u la phah ïa u nongkhrai khlieh, bad u la hukum ban wallam ïa ka khlieh jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba u la leit, u la khrai khlieh ïa u ha ka byndi, bad u la wallam ïa ka khlieh jong u ha ka pliang, bad u la ai ïa ka ha kata ka khynnah: bad kata ka khynnah ka la ai ïa ka ha ka kmie jong ka.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba ki synran jong u ki la ïohsngew, ki la wan bad ki la rah noh ïa ka met jong u, bad ki la tep ïa ka ha ka jingtep.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki apostol ki la ïalum lang ha U Jisu, bad ki la ïathuh ïa kiei kiei baroh ha u, kat kiba ki la lah leh, bad kat kiba ki la lah hikai.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “To ale ma phi hi kyrpang sha ri khlaw, bad shongthait khyndiat”: naba don shibun kiba ïawan ïaleit ruh, katba kim kloi shuh wat ban bam ruh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta, ki la leit noh da ka lieng sha ka jaka kynjah kyrpang hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, ki paidbah ki la ïohi ïa ki ba ki dang leit, shibun ruh ki la ithuh ïa ki; te ki la phet lang hangta na sha ryngkew na ki shnong baroh, bad ki la shuwa ïa ki, bad ki la ïawan lang sha u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la mih noh, u la ïohi ïa u paidbah babun, bad u la sngewsynei ïa ki, naba ki long kum ki langbrot khlem u nongsharai; te u la sdang ban hikai bun kiei kiei ruh ïa ki.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Haba ka la noh eh ïan ka sngi, te ki synran jong u ki la wan ha u, bad ki ong, “Kane ka long ka jaka kynjah, bad ka sngi ka la noh eh ïan ruh;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> to pyllait noh ïa ki, ba kin ïoh leit kylleng sawdong sha ki ri bri bad sha ki shnong rit ban thied jingbam ïa lade, naba kim don ei ei ruh ban bam.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “To ai ma phi ba kin bam.” Ki te ki ong ha u, “Hato ngin leit ïathied arspah suka u kpu, bad ai ruh ha ki ban bam?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U ong te ha ki, “Katno tylli ki kpu phi don? Khie leit khmih.” Haba ki la tip, ki ong, “San, bad ar tylli ki dohkha.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U la hukum te ïa ki, ba baroh kin shong shaniah lynnong lynnong halor u phlang bajyrngam.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ki la shong shaniah ter ter, shispah shispah, bad sanphew sanphew ruh.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Haba u la shim te ïa kita san tylli ki kpu bad ïa kita ar tylli ki dohkha ruh, haba u la khmied sha bneng, u la nguh, bad u la kdiah ruh ïa ki kpu, bad u la ai ha ki synran jong u, ba kin buh ha khmat jong ki; bad ïa kita ki dohkha u la ïasam ha ki baroh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Baroh ki la ïabam, bad ki la ïakdang ruh.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad ki la ïakhar ruh dap khat-ar tukri, na kiba lwet bad na ki dohkha ruh.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kita te kiba la ïabam ïa kita ki kpu, ki long jin san hajar ki rangbah.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, u la phah ïa ki synran jong u ba kin kiew halor ka lieng, bad ban nang leit shuwa sha shiliang sha Bethsaida, katba u hi u nang pyllait ïa u paidbah.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ynda u la bidai noh te ïa ki, u la leit sha u lum ban duwai.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Haba la janmiet, kata ka lieng ka la don hapdeng ka duriaw, u te tang weibriew hi ha ryngkew.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U la ïohi te ïa ki, ba ki shitom da kaba ki ïaking, naba ka lyer ka la beh pyrshah ïa ki: te hamar ka jingap miet ka basaw, u wan ha ki, u da ïaid halor duriaw; bad u la leh kum ban sa ïaid kiar ïa ki.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Hynrei, ki, haba ki la ïohi ïa u ba u ïaid halor duriaw, ki la ïamut ba ka la long rngai, bad ki la ïalynñiar jam ruh,",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> naba baroh ki la ïohi ïa u, bad ki ïasngewkyiuh eh. Hynrei, kumne kumne ruh, u la kren ha ki, bad u ong ha ki, “To long shlur, dei ma nga, to wat sheptieng.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Bad u la kiew sha ki halor kata ka lieng; te kata ka lyer ka la jem jai: hangta ki la sngewkyndit noh shikatdei eh ha lade, bad ki la sngewphylla.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Naba kim shym sngewthuh shaphang kita ki kpu; hynrei, ka dohnud jong ki ka la long kaba eh.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Haba ki la poi te sha shiliang, ki la wan ha ka ri Gennesaret, te hangta ki la kiew sha ryngkew.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Haba ki la mih noh te na kata ka lieng, ki la ithuh ïa u kumne kumne ruh,",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> bad haba ki la ïaphet kylleng sawdong kata ka ri baroh, ki la sdang ban ïabah na kylleng ha ki jingthiah ïa kiba la pang, kat shaba ki la sngew ba u don.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Shano shano ba u leit bsut ruh sha ki nongrit, lane sha ki nongbah, lane sha ki ri bri, ki la buh ïa ki bapang ha ki jaka ïew, bad ki la kyrpad ïa u, ba kin shu ïoh ktah ïa ka rmiang ka jaiñ jong u: te kat kiba la ïoh ktah ïa u, la pynkhiah ïa ki phar."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Pharisi ki la ïawan lang ha u, bad kiba na ki nongthoh, kiba la wan na Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba ki la ïohi te ïa kiba na ki synran jong u, ba ki bam ja da ki kti bymkhuid (kata, khlem da thet satia), ki la pynrem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> (Naba ki Pharisi bad ki Jiw baroh, lymda ki ïoh thet bha ïa la ki kti, kim bam satia, ki da bat skhem ïa ka rukom pateng la pateng ki tymmen basan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haba ki wan ruh na ïew, lymda ki ïoh sum, kim bam satia. Bad bun kiwei kiwei pat ruh don, ïa kiba ki la pdiang ban bat skhem, kum ki jingsait ki khuri, bad ki luta, bad ki pliang, bad ki palong ruh).",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, kita ki Pharisi bad kita ki nongthoh ki la kylli ïa u, “Balei ba ki synran jong me kim ïaid kat kum ka rukom pateng la pateng ki tymmen basan, hynrei, ki bam ja da ki kti kiba khlem thet?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la ïathuh te ha ki, “Ka dei kaba u Isaïah u la ïathuhlypa shaphang jong phi kiba arsap, kumba la thoh: “ ‘Kine ki briew ki burom ïa nga da la ki rmiang shyntur, hynrei, ka dohnud jong ki te ka jngai na nga:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hynrei, ki mane thala ïa nga, haba ki hikai kum ki jinghikai ïa ki hukum jong ki briew’:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Naba haba phi iehnoh ïa ka hukum U Blei, phi bat skhem ïa ka rukom pateng la pateng ki briew, kum ki jingsait ki luta bad ki khuri: bad ïa bun kiei kiei ruh kiwei pat kum kine phi leh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Phi kyntait la biang keiñ ïa ka hukum U Blei, ba phin ïoh sumar ïa ka rukom pateng la pateng jong phi;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> naba u Moses u la ong, ‘Burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie’; bad, ‘Jar uba krenbeiñ ïa u kpa lane ïa ka kmie, un ïap da shisha’;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> hynrei, phi ong, ‘Lada u briew un ong ïa la u kpa lane ïa la ka kmie, Kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba men myntoi na nga ka long “Korban” (kata long, “ka jingainguh”), un lait;’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> phim shah shuh te ïa u ban leh ei ei ruh em ïa u kpa jong u, lane ïa ka kmie jong u;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> phi da pynduh ïa ka ktien U Blei da ka rukom pateng la pateng jong phi, ïa kaba phi hikai: bad shibun kiei kiei ruh kum kine phi leh.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u la khot ha u ïa uta u paidbah baroh, u la ong ruh ha ki, “To sngap ïa nga phi baroh, to sngewthuh ruh:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ym don ei ei ruh shabar u briew, kaba leit hapoh jong u, ba lah ban pyntngit ïa u: hynrei, kiei kiei ruh kiba mih noh na u briew, kita keiñ, ki long kiba pyntngit ïa u briew:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> lada uno uno ruh u don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u la leit hapoh ïing na uta u paidbah, ki synran jong u ki la kylli ïa u shaphang kata ka pharshi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U ong te ha ki, “Phi ruh phi long kumta ki bym sngewthuh? Phim shemphang, ba baroh kaba shabar kaba leit shapoh u briew, kam lah ban pyntngit ïa u?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> naba kam leit shapoh ka dohnud jong u, hynrei, sha ka kpoh, bad ka mih noh na ka, sharud”: ba ki khuid ki jingbam baroh keiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U la ong ruh, “Kata kaba mih noh na u briew, kata keiñ, ka pyntngit ïa u briew:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> naba na shapoh, na ka dohnud ki briew, ki mih noh ki jingmut bymman, kiba klim, kiba ïakai kynthei, kiba pynïap,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> kiba tuh, kiba kurup, kiba pynsniew, kaba arsap, kaba nuti, kaba khwan lalot, kaba khmih sniew, kaba krenbeiñ, kaba sngewkhraw, bad kaba leh bieit:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> kine kiei kiei baroh ki bymman ki mih noh na shapoh, bad ki pyntngit ïa u briew.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba u la ïeng, u la leit noh nangta ruh sha ki phang ka Tyros bad ka Sidon; bad haba u la leit hapoh ka ïing, um kwah ïano ïano ruh ban tip, hynrei, um lah ban long ha kaba rieh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba don ka kynthei, kaba ka khun rit jong ka, ka don mynsiem bymkhuid, haba ka la ïohsngew shaphang jong u, ka la wan bad ka la dem ha ki kjat jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kata ka kynthei te ka la long ka Grik, ka kynja Syrophinisa, bad ka la kyrpad ïa u, ba un beh noh ïa uta u ksuid na ka khun jong ka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha ka, “Ai ban pynkdang shuwa ïa ki khun; naba ym dei ban shim ïa ka jingbam jong ki khun, bad ban bred ha ki ksew.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, ka la ïathuh bad ka la ong ha u, “Shisha, ko Trai, wat kita ki ksew hapoh ka miej ki bam na kiba lwet jong ki khun.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “Namar kane ka jingong, to khie leit noh; uta u ksuid u la mih noh na ka khun jong pha.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ka la leit noh sha la ïing, bad ka la shem ïa la ka khun ba la pynthiah ïa ka ha ka jingthiah, bad ba la mih noh uta u ksuid.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ynda U la leit noh pat na ki phang ka Tyros bad ka Sidon, U la wan poi sha ka duriaw Galilaïa, napdeng ki phang Dekapolis.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki wallam ha U ïa u bakyllut bad bakren thlun; ki kyrpad ruh ïa U ba un buh ïa la ka kti ha u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te haba U la shim noh ïa u kyrpang weibriew na uta u paidbah, U la buh ïa la ki shynriah'ti ha ki shkor jong u, bad haba U la lah biah, U la ktah ïa u thylliej jong u;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad haba U la khmied sha bneng, U la ud, bad U ong ïa u, “Ephphatha,” kata ban ong, “To long ba la plie”.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, la plie noh ïa ki shkor jong u, bad la lait ka jingteh u thylliej jong u, bad u la nang kren beit.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U la hukum te ïa ki, ba kin ym ïathuh hano hano ruh, hynrei, katba U la nang adong ïa ki, katta ki la nang ïa-pynbna kham tam pynban.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ki la sngewkyndit bym lah ong shuh, ki da ong, “Ka bha baroh kat kaba U la leh; naba U pynlong ïa ki bakyllut ban sngew, bad ïa ki bymnangkren ban kren.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, mynba la don pat u paidbah babun eh, bad ba kim don ei ei ruh ban bam, U Jisu u la khot ha u ïa ki synran jong u, bad u ong ha ki,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Nga sngewsynei ïa u paidbah; naba mynta la lai sngi ki la ïashong bad nga, bad kim don shuh ei ei ruh ban bam:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> lada ngan phah noh jingit ïa ki sha la ïing, kin ïap tyrsaw noh ha lynti; naba na ki don kiba la wan na sha jngai.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki synran jong u te ki la ïathuh ha u, “Nangno yn lah ban pynkdang ïa kine da u kpu hangne ha ka jaka kynjah?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la kylli ïa ki, “Phi don katno ki kpu?” Bad ki la ong, “Hynñiew tylli.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la hukum te ïa uta u paidbah ban shong ha khyndew: te haba u la shim ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki kpu, bad ba u la lah nguh, u la kdiah, bad u la ai ha ki synran jong u, ban buh ha khmat jong ki; ki ruh ki la buh ha khmat uta u paidbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la don ruh khyndiat ki dohkha rit: te haba u la lah kyrkhu, u la ong ban buh ïa kita ruh ha khmat jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ki la ïabam, bad ki la kdang: bad ki la ïakhar hynñiew tukri na kiba lwet kiba la sah tam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kita kiba la ïabam te ki don kumba saw hajar: bad u la phah noh ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, haba u la leit ha ka lieng lem bad ki synran jong u, u la wan sha ki phang ka Dalmanutha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki Pharisi ki la mih noh, bad ki la sdang ban ïakylli nia ïa u, ba ki ïawad na u ka dak na bneng, ki da ïatynjuh ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba u la ud jylliew te ha la ka mynsiem, u la ong, “Balei ba kane ka pateng bynriew ka wad ïa ka dak? Shisha nga ong ha phi, yn ym ai ka dak ha kane ka pateng bynriew.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u la iehnoh ïa ki, u la kiew pat ha kata ka lieng, bad u la leit noh sha shiliang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki la klet ban wallam kpu, lymne kim shym don lem bad ki nalor uwei u kpu ha kata ka lieng.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “To sumar, to kiar na u thiat ki Pharisi, bad na u thiat u Herod.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki te ki la ïakren hi paralok, ki da ong, “Ba ngim don kpu.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la tip, u ong ha ki, “Balei phi ïakren naba phim don kpu? phim pat puson, lymne sngewthuh? phi dang don ka dohnud jong phi kaba eh?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> haba phi don ki khmat, phim ïohi? haba phi don ki shkor ruh, phim ïohsngew? phim kynmaw ruh?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mynba nga la kdiah ïa ki san tylli ki kpu ha kita san hajar, dap katno tukri na kiba lwet phi la ïakhar?” Ki ong ha u, “Khat-ar.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Bad mynba ïa kita hynñiew tylli ha kita saw hajar, dap katno tukri na kiba lwet phi la ïakhar?” Ki la ong ruh, “Hynñiew.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Kumno ba phim pat sngewthuh?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki wan ruh sha Bethsaida; te ki wallam ha U ïa u bamatlah, bad ki ïakyrpad ïa U ban ktah ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba U la bat ïa uta u bamatlah na ka kti, U la ïalam noh ïa u shabar kata ka shnong; bad haba U la biah ha ki khmat jong u, bad ba U la buh ïa ki kti ha u, U la kylli ïa u, “Me ïohi ei ei?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba u la khmied te, u la ong, “Nga ïohi ki briew kum ki dieng ba ki ïaid.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hadien kata, U la buh pat ïa la ki kti ha ki khmat jong u; bad U la pynkhmied ïa u; te la pynbha pat ïa u, bad u la ïohi shynna ïa kiei kiei baroh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad U la phah ïa u sha la ïing, U da ong, “Wat rung satia sha kato ka shnong.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te U Jisu u la leit noh bad ki synran jong u, sha ki nongrit jong ka Kaisaria Philippi: bad ha lynti u la kylli ïa ki synran jong u, u da ong ha ki, “Ïa nga, ki briew ki ong ba nga long uei?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki la ïathuh te, “U Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis: kiwei, U Elias; kiwei pat de, Uwei na ki nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u kylli ïa ki, “Hynrei, phi, phi ong ba nga long uei?” U Petros u ïathuh, u ong ha U, “Me long uta U Khrist.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U la hukum skhem te ïa ki, ba kin ym ïathuh hano hano ruh shaphang jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u la sdang ban hikai ïa ki, ba ka dei ïa U Khun u briew ban shah shibun kiei kiei ruh, bad ba yn kyntait da ki tymmen basan, bad ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ki nongthoh, bad ba yn pynïap ruh; bad hadien lai sngi un mihpat.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ha kaba paw shynna ruh u la kren ïa kata ka jingong. Haba u Petros te u la shim kyrpang ïa U, u la sdang ban sneng ïa U.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, haba U la phai, bad ba U da khmih ha ki synran jong U, U la sneng ïa u Petros, U da ong, “Khie leit shadien jong nga, me u Soitan: naba mem ñiew ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong U Blei, hynrei, tang ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong ki briew.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba U la khot ha U ïa u paidbah lem bad ki synran jong u, u la ong ha ki, “Jar uba mon ban wan bud nadien jong nga, ai ba un len ïa lade, bad un bah ïa la ka diengphna, bad un bud ïa nga:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> naba uno uno ruh u ban mon ban pynim ïa la ka mynsiem, un duh noh ïa ka; uno uno ruh u ban duh noh te ïa la ka mynsiem, na ka bynta jong nga bad ka jong ka gospel ruh, uta keiñ, un shem ïa ka.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Naba u briew un myntoi aïu, lada un ïoh ïa ka pyrthei baroh, bad un duh noh ïa la ka mynsiem?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> naba u briew un ai aïu ban ïapeiñ ïa la ka mynsiem?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> naba uno uno ruh u ban sngewlehrain ïa nga bad ïa ki ktien jong nga, ha kane ka pateng bynriew baklim bad bapop, U Khun u briew ruh un lehrain ïa uta, haba u wan ha ka burom U Kpa jong u, lem bad ki angel bakhuid.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba don kiba na kine kiba ïeng hangne, ki ban ym mad ïa ka jingïap, tad ynda ki la ïohi ïa ka hima U Blei ba ka la wan da ka bor.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda la hynriew sngi te U Jisu u shim lem ïa u Petros, bad ïa u Jakob, bad ïa u Ïoannis, bad u leit lam ïa ki sha u lum bajrong kyrpang hi; bad la pynkylla dur ïa u ha khmat jong ki,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ki jaiñ jong u te ki la long kiba tyngshaiñ, kiba lieh eh, kat kata ruh ym don u nongpynkhuid jaiñ ha ka pyrthei uba lah ban pynlieh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La paw ruh ha ki u Elias lem bad u Moses, bad ki da ïakren bad U Jisu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba u Petros u ïathuh te u ong ha U Jisu, “Ko Kynrad, ka bha ïa ngi ban don hangne; ai ngin ïathaw te lai tylli ki ïing dara, kawei ïa me, kawei ruh ïa u Moses, bad kawei ruh ïa u Elias.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naba um tip ïa-ei ba un kren, naba ki la sheptieng eh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te la wan u lyoh uba kah ïa ki, bad ka ktien ka la wan na uta u lyoh, ka da ong, “Une u long U Khun jong nga uba ieit, to phin sngew ïa u.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kyndit kyndit haba ki la khmih kylleng sawdong, kim ïohi shuh ïano ïano ruh, hynrei, tang ïa U Jisu hi lem bad ki hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki dang hiar na uta u lum, u la hukum skhem ïa ki, ba kin ym ïathuh hano hano ruh ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba ki la ïohi, tad ynda U Khun u briew u la mihpat na ki baïap.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki la ïabat skhem te ïa kata ka ktien, ba ki da ïakylli paralok hi, “Ka long aïu kata, ‘ban mihpat na ki baïap.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Balei ba ki ong ki nongthoh ba ka dei ïa u Elias ban wan shuwa?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u da ïathuh, u la ong ha ki, “U Elias shisha u wan shuwa, bad u pynbha ïa kiei kiei baroh ruh; bad kumno la thoh shaphang U Khun u briew? ba un shah bun kiei kiei ruh, bad ba yn ñiewbeiñ ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba u Elias u la wan, bad ki la leh ïa u katba ki la imon, kumba la thoh shaphang jong u.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Haba ki la wan te sha ki synran, ki la ïohi ïa u paidbah babun tawiar ïa ki, bad ïa ki nongthoh ruh ba ki ïasaid bad ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, uta u paidbah baroh, haba ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la sngewkyndit eh, bad haba ki la phet sha u, ki la nguh ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U la kylli te ïa ki, “Ïa-ei ba phi ïasaid bad ki?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uwei te na uta u paidbah u la ïathuh, u la ong ruh, “Ko Nonghikai, nga la wallam ha me ïa u khun jong nga, uba don u mynsiem bymnangkren;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> shaei shaei ruh ba u lap ïa u, u lympat ïa u, te u sei tyrtho, bad u kyr-iat ïa la ki bniat, bad u nangswai ruh: nga la ong te ha ki synran jong me ba kin beh noh ïa u, te kim lah satia.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te U ïathuh bad U ong ha ki, “A phi ka pateng bynriew bymngeit, sa katno ngan long bad phi? Sa katno ngan shah ïa phi? To wallam ïa u ha nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki la wallam te ïa u ha U, bad haba u la ïohi ïa U, kumne kumne ruh, uta u mynsiem u la ring kyrthat ïa u; bad haba u la kyllon ha ka khyndew, u la ksaid, u da sei tyrtho ruh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la kylli te ïa u kpa jong u, “Ka la slem katno naduh ba la jia kane ha u?” U la ïathuh te, “Naduh ba dang khynnah;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> u ju pynnoh jyndei ruh ïa u ha ka ding bad ha ki um, ban pynjot ïa u: hynrei, lada me lah ei ei ruh, to isynei ïa ngi, bad to ïarap ïa ngi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u te, “Lada me lah ban ngeit! Kiei kiei baroh ki long kiba lah ïa uta uba ngeit.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, haba u kpa uta u khynnah u la ïam jam, u la ong bad ki jingjaw ummat ruh, “Nga ngeit, A Trai; to ïarap ïa ka jingbymngeit jong nga.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohi ba u paidbah u ïaphet lang sha U, U la sneng ïa uta u mynsiem bymkhuid, U da ong ha u, “Ko mynsiem bymnangkren bad bakyllut, nga hukum ïa me, ‘To mih noh na u, wat leit bsut shuh ruh ha u.’ ”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Haba u la lynñiar te, bad u la ring kyrthat ïa u shikatdei, u la mih noh bad uta u khynnah u la long kum uba la ïap, katba shibun ki ong, “Ba u la ïap.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu haba u la bat ïa u na ka kti, U la khyllie ïa u, u de u la ïeng joit.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Haba U la leit te hapoh ïing, ki synran jong U ki la kylli ïa U jar jar, “Balei ba ngi ngim lah ban beh noh ïa u?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ïa u kynja une ym lah ban pynmih noh da ei da ei ruh em, hynrei, tang da ka jingduwai bad ka jingit.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Haba ki la ïaleit noh nangta ruh, ki la ïa-ïaid lyngba ïa ka Galilaïa; um mon te ïano ïano ruh ban tip.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Naba u la hikai ïa ki synran jong u, bad u la ong ha ki, “Yn sa aiti noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki briew, bad kin pynïap ïa u, te haba la pynïap, un sa mihpat ha ka balai sngi.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, kim shemphang ïa kata ka jingong, bad ki la sheptieng ban kylli ïa u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U la poi ruh ha Kapernam: te haba u dang don ha ïing, u la kylli ïa ki, “Kaei ba phi la ïasaid paralok ha lynti?”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ki la shu sngap, naba ki la lah ïasaid hi paralok ha lynti, uei u ban kham khraw.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Haba u la shong te u la khot ïa ki khat-ar ngut, bad u la ong ha ki, “Lada uno uno ruh u kwah ban long shuwa, un long u bakhatduh na ki baroh, bad u shakri jong ki baroh.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Haba U la shim te ïa u khynnah, U la pynïeng ïa u hapdeng jong ki; bad haba U la shim kynthup ïa u, U la ong ha ki,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “Uno uno ruh u ban pdiang ïa uwei na kum kine ki khynnah ha ka kyrteng jong nga, u pdiang ïa nga: bad uno uno ruh uba pdiang ïa nga, um pdiang ïa nga hi, hynrei, ïa uta keiñ uba la phah ïa nga.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U Ïoannis u la ong ha u, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi la ïohi ïa uwei uba beh noh ïa ki ksuid ha ka kyrteng jong me; te ngi la adong ïa u, namar um ïabud lok bad ngi.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong, “Wat adong shuh ïa u; naba ym don uba leh ïa ka kambah ha ka kyrteng jong nga, uba lah shen ruh ban kren sniew ïa nga:",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> naba jar u bym ïaleh ïa ngi, u long ha ka liang jong ngi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Naba uno uno ruh u ban ai ha phi ban dih shi khuri ka um ha ka kyrteng jong nga, namar ba phi long ki jong U Khrist, shisha nga ong ha phi, un ym duh da lei lei ïa la ka nong.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> “Jar u ban pynthut te ïa uwei na kine ki barit kiba ngeit ha nga, ka la kham bha ïa u lada la teh da u mawtylliat bakhraw ha ka ryndang jong u, bad la bred ruh ïa u ha duriaw.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Lada ka kti jong me te ka pynthut ïa me, to ot noh ïa ka: ka bha ïa me ban leit bsut dkoh sha ka jingim, ban ïa kaba me don ar tylli ki kti ban leit sha dujok, sha ka ding bymjulip,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> sha kaba u ksaiñ jong ki um ïap, bad ka ding kam ju lip.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Lada ka kjat jong me ruh ka pynthut ïa me, to ot noh ïa ka: ka bha ïa me ban leit bsut dkoh sha ka jingim, ban ïa kaba me don ar tylli ki kjat ban bred ïa me ha dujok, sha ka ding bymjulip,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> sha kaba u ksaiñ jong ki, um ïap, bad ka ding, kam ju lip.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Lada ka khmat jong me ruh ka pynthut ïa me, to khlaw noh ïa ka: ka bha ïa me ban leit bsut sha ka hima U Blei tang da kawei ka khmat, ban ïa kaba me don ar tylli ki khmat ba'n bred ïa me ha dujok ding,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> sha kaba u ksaiñ jong ki, um ïap, bad ka ding, kam ju lip.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Naba ïa u briew baroh yn kyllan mluh da ka ding, kumba kyllan mluh da ka mluh ïa ka jingkñia baroh.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ka mluh ka bha: hynrei, lada kata ka mluh ka la kylla blad, te da ei phin pynthiang pat ïa ka? To phin ïadon mluh ha lade lade, to phin ïasuk ruh paralok hi.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Haba u la mih nangta, u la wan ha ki phang Judia, sha shiliang ka Jordan: bad ki paidbah ki la ïalum lang pat ha u; te kumba u la ju leh, u la hikai pat ïa ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te don na ki Pharisi kiba la wan ha u, bad ki la kylli ïa u, “Ka bit ne em ïa u briew ban pyllait noh ïa la ka tnga?” ba ki ïatynjuh ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U da ïathuh u la ong te ha ki, “Kaei ba u Moses u la hukum ïa phi?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “U Moses u la shah ban thoh ïa ka kot iehnoh, bad ban ïapyllait noh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Namar ka dohnud runar jong phi u la thoh ïa phi ïa kane ka hukum:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hynrei, la myndanglong ka pyrthei, ‘Shynrang bad kynthei U Blei u la thaw ïa ki:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ka bynta kane, u briew un iehnoh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad un ïaineh bad la ka tnga;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ki baroh ar ngut te kin ïalong kawei ka doh. Kumta, kim long ar ngut shuh, hynrei, kawei ka doh.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, ïa kaba U Blei u la pynïasoh lem, to u briew wat pynïakhlad.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda ha ïing, ki synran jong u ki la kylli pat ïa u shaphang kata kajuh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U ong te ha ki, “Uno uno ruh u ban iehnoh ïa la ka tnga, bad u ban shongkurim ïa kawei pat, u klim ïa ka:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> lada kata ruh kan iehnoh ïa la u tnga, bad kan shongkurim ïa uwei pat, ka klim.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la wallam ïa ki khunlung ha u, ba un ïoh ktah ïa ki, ki synran te ki la sneng ïa kita kiba ïawallam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, haba U Jisu u la ïohi ïa kata, u la sngewsih eh, bad u la ong ha ki, “To shah ïa ki khunlung ban wan ha nga, to wat khang ruh ïa ki: naba ïa kiba kum kita, long ka hima U Blei.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, uno uno ruh u ban ym pdiang ïa ka hima U Blei kum u khun khynnah, un ym leit bsut hapoh kata.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u la shim kynthup ïa ki, u la buh ïa la ki kti ha ki, u da kyrkhu ïa ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba U dang leit te nangta sha lynti bah, uwei u la phet ha U bad u la dem khohsiew ha U, bad u la kylli ïa U, “Ko Nonghikai babha, kaei ngan leh ba ngan ïoh ka jingim bymjukut?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Jisu u la ong te ha u, “Balei ba me khot babha ïa nga? Ym don u babha, hynrei, tang uwei, uba U Blei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Me tip ïa ki hukum: ‘Wat klim, wat pynïap, wat tuh, wat sakhi lamler, wat leh klop, burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie ruh.’ ”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ïathuh ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, ïa kita baroh nga la sumar la myndang khynnah.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Jisu te haba U la khmih ha u, U la sngewieit ïa u, bad U la ong ha u, “Kawei ka dang duna ïa me: to khie leit, die noh katba me don, ai ruh ha ki baduk, te men ïoh ka jingkynshew ha bneng: te ale, da rah ïa ka diengphna, to bud ruh ïa nga.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u la buhkhoh namar kata ka ktien, bad u la leit noh sngewsih, naba u la don shibun ki spah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la khmih baroh sawdong, u la ong ha ki synran jong u, “A, kaba da eh ïa kiba don spah, ba kin leit bsut ha ka hima U Blei!”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki synran te ki la kyndit thred namar kita ki ktien jong u. Hynrei, U Jisu u da ïathuh pat, u ong ha ki, “Ko khun, ew! kaba da eh ïa kita kiba shaniah ha ki spah, ban leit bsut ha ka hima U Blei!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka long kaba kham jem ïa ka ut ban bsut lyngba ïa ka thliew thyrnia, ban ïa u bariewspah ban leit bsut ha ka hima U Blei.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki te ki la nang sngewkyndit shikatdei eh, ki da ïa-ong ha u, “Te kumta uei ba lah ban lait im?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Haba U Jisu u la khmih shaiñ te ha ki, u la ong, “Ha ki briew, kata ka bym lah; hynrei, ym ha U Blei: naba kiei kiei baroh ki long kiba lah ha U Blei.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, u Petros u la sdang ban ong ha U, “Ha khmih, ngi la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh, ngi la bud ruh ïa me.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u da ïathuh u la ong, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ym don uba la iehnoh ïa ka ïing, lane ïa ki hynmen hynbew shynrang ne kynthei, lane ïa u kpa lane ïa ka kmie, lane ïa ka tnga lane ïa ki khun, lane ïa ki bri, na ka bynta jong nga bad jong ka gospel,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> hynrei, un ïoh diang keiñ shispah shah ïa katta mynta ha kane ka por, ïa ki ïing, bad ïa ki hynmen hynbew shynrang bad kynthei, bad ïa ki kmie, bad ïa ki khun, bad ïa ki bri de, lem bad ki jinglehbeiñ; bad ha ka pyrthei ka ban sa wan, ka jingim bymjukut.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, shibun ki bashuwa kin long khatduh, bad ki bakhatduh kin long shuwa.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki ïadon te ha lynti ba ki da ïaleit kiew sha Jerusalem, bad U Jisu u la ïaid ha shuwa jong ki: bad ki la kyndit eh, bad kita kiba bud ki la sheptieng. Haba u da shim pat ruh ïa ki khat-ar ngut, u la sdang ban ïathuh ha ki, ïa kiei kiei ki ban sa jia ha u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Naba, ha khmih, ngi ïaleit kiew sha Jerusalem, te ïa U Khun u briew yn sa ai noh ha ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ha ki nongthoh; bad kin pynrem ïa u ïa ka ban ïap, bad kin ai noh ruh ïa u ha ki Jentil:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ki te kin lehbeiñ ïa u, bad kin bynthiew ïa u, bad kin sympat ïa u, bad kin pynïap noh ïa u; hynrei, ha ka balai sngi un mihpat.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Jakob bad u Ïoannis, ki khun u Sebedi, ki la wan te ha u, ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi kwah ba men leh ïa ngi ïa kaei kaei ba ngin sa pan na me.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Kaei ba phi kwah ïa nga ban leh ïa phi?”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ki la ong te ha u, “To ai ïa ngi ba ngin shong, uwei sha kamon jong me bad uwei pat sha kadiang jong me, ha ka burom jong me.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Phim tip kaei ba phi pan. Phi lah ban dih na kata ka khuri na kaba ngan sa dih, bad ba yn pynbaptis ïa phi ruh da kata ka jingbaptis da kaba yn sa pynbaptis ïa nga?”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te ki la ong ha u, “Ngi lah.” Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Ïa kata ka khuri, na kaba ngan sa dih, phin dih shisha, bad da kata ka jingbaptis da kaba yn sa pynbaptis ïa nga, yn pynbaptis ïa phi ruh;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> hynrei, ban shong sha kamon jong nga bad sha kadiang jong nga, kam long ka jong nga ban ai, hynrei, ka long ïa kita ïa kiba la pynkhreh ïa ka.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te haba kita ki shiphew ngut ki la ïohsngew, ki la sdang ban ïasngewsih ïa u Jakob bad ïa u Ïoannis.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te U Jisu haba u la khot ïa ki ha u, u ong ha ki, “Phi tip ba kita kiba ki ïañiew ban synshar ïa ki Jentil, ki leh trai khlieh ïa ki; bad ki bakhraw batri na ki, ki leh bor ïa ki:",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> hynrei, kan ym long kumta hapdeng jong phi; hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban kwah ban long bakhraw hapdeng jong phi, un long u shakri jong phi,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad uno uno ruh na phi u ban kwah ban long rangbah, un long u mraw jong phi baroh;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> naba shisha U Khun u briew um shym la wan ban ïoh shakri, hynrei, ban shakri, bad ban ai la ka jingim ban long ka jingsiewspah na ka bynta kiba bun.”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te ki la wan poi ha Jerikho; haba u dang leit noh ruh na Jerikho bad ki synran jong u bad u paidbah babun de, u Bartimaïos u bamatlah, u khun u Timaïos, u la shong harud lynti, ba u da makia.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Haba u la ïohsngew te ba dei U Jisu uba na Nasaret, u la sdang ban kyrpad jam, ban ong ruh, “Ko Jisu me U Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa nga!”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bun te ki la sneng ïa u, ba un sngap jar, hynrei, u la kyrpad jam kham tam, “Me U Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa nga!”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> U Jisu haba U la ïeng te, U la ong, “To khot ïa u.” Bad ki khot ïa uta u bamatlah, ki da ong ha u, “To kyrmen, to ïeng ruh, U khot ïa me.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> U ruh u da buh noh bak ïa la ka jaiñkup, haba u la ïeng joit, u la wan ha U Jisu.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh te U la ong ha u, “Me kwah ba ngan leh aïu ïa me?” Uta u bamatlah u la ong te ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, ba ngan ïoh imat.”",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U Jisu u la ong te ha u, “To khie leit noh, kata ka jingngeit jong me ka la pynkhiah ïa me;” te kumne kumne ruh, u la ïoh imat, bad u la bud ïa U ha kata ka lynti."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda ki la poi hajan Jerusalem, sha Bethphage bad Bethania, haduh u lum ki Olib, u phah ar ngut na ki synran jong u,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u ong ha ki, “Khie leit sha ka shnong kaba ha marpyrshah jong phi: te phi tang shu poi ha ka, phin shem ïa u khun kadda ba la teh, u bym pat ju don u briew ba la shong; to pyllait ïa u, bad to wallam noh ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te lada uno uno ruh un ong ha phi, ‘Balei phi leh kumne?’ phin ong ‘ba U Trai u donkam ïa u, te kumne kumne ruh, un phah noh ïa u hangne.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la leit noh, bad ki la shem ïa uta u khun kadda ba la teh ha ka jingkhang habar, ha lynti shnong; te ki pyllait ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kiba na kita te kiba ïeng hangta, ki la ong ha ki, “Phi leh aïu, ba phi pyllait ïa uta u khun kadda?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki la ong te ha ki kumba U Jisu u la lah hukum, te ki la shah ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la wallam te ïa uta u khun kadda ha U Jisu, bad ki la siang halor jong u ïa ki jaiñkup jong ki; bad U la shong halor jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bun ruh ki la siang ïa ki jaiñkup jong ki ha ka lynti; kiwei te ki la khyllad ïa ki tnat dieng, bad ki la siang ha kata ka lynti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kita kiba ïaid sha shuwa, bad kita kiba bud nadien de, ki la ïapyrta, “Hosanna! Long ba la kyrkhu uta uba wan ha ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Long kaba la kyrkhu kata ka hima kaba wan, ka hima ka jong u Dabid u kpa jong ngi keiñ. Hosanna ha kiba jrong tam eh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Jisu u la leit ruh shapoh Jerusalem, shapoh ka templ; te haba u la khmih baroh sawdong ïa kiei kiei baroh, ba ka long lypa ruh janmiet, u la leit noh sha Bethania lem bad ki khat-ar ngut.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ha kaba lashai te, haba ki la mih noh na Bethania, U la sngewthngan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba U la ïohi te ïa u dieng Dumbur na jngai, ba u don ki sla, U la leit ban khmih la un shem ei ei ha u; haba U la poi te ha u, um shym la shem ei ei ruh, hynrei, tang ki sla, naba kam pat long ka aïom soh Dumbur.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U Jisu u la ïathuh bad U la ong ha u, “Ym don u ban bam soh shuh na me lano lano ruh!” Ki synran jong U ki la ïohsngew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la poi ha Jerusalem. Te haba u la leit shapoh ka templ, u la sdang ban beh noh ïa kita kiba ïadie ïathied ha ka templ; bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki miej jong ki nongïapeiñ sbai, bad ïa ki jingshong jong kita kiba ïadie paro,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad um shah ïano ïano ruh ban rah jingdiang ei ei lyngba ïa ka templ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la hikai ruh, u da ong ha ki, “Ym shym la thoh: ‘Ïa ka ïing jong nga yn khot ka ïing jingduwai ïa ki briew baroh’? Hynrei, phi, ka krem nongtuh phi la pynlong ïa ka.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki nongthoh bad ki rangbah lyngdoh te ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, bad ki la ïawad dong kumno ba kin pynïap noh ïa U, namar ki la sheptieng ïa U. Hynrei, u paidbah baroh u la kyndit thred na ka jinghikai jong U.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te janmiet janmiet u la leit noh shabar ka shnong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Haba ki la ïaid lait mynstep ruh, ki la ïohi ïa uta u dieng Dumbur ba la ïap tyrkhong naduh ki thied.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Petros te haba u da kynmaw pat u ong ha U, “Ko Kynrad, ha khmih, uta u dieng Dumbur ïa uba me la tim, u la ïap tyrkhong noh!”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh u ong te ha ki, “To ïoh ma phi ka jingngeit ha U Blei.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba uno uno ruh u ban ong ha une u lum, ‘To long ba la rat noh, to noh ruh sha duriaw’, bad un ym sngew-artatien ha la ka dohnud, hynrei, un ngeit ba yn sa long kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba u la ong, kan long ïa u kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba un ong.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar kata, nga ong ha phi, ba kiei kiei baroh kat kiba phi pan, haba phi kyrpad, to ngeit ba phi pdiang ïa kita, te phin sa ïoh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Haba phi da ïeng kyrpad ruh, to map, lada phi bat sngewsih ïano ïano ruh, ba U Kpa jong phi ruh uba ha bneng un map ïa phi ïa ki ryngkang jong phi:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> hynrei, lada phi phim ïamap, te U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng un ym map ïa ki ryngkang jong phi.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki wan pat sha Jerusalem: te katba u dang ïaid ha ka templ, ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ki nongthoh, bad ki tymmen basan ruh ki wan ha u,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ki ong ha u, “Da ka bor aïu me leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh? bad la ai mano ha me ïa kane ka bor ban leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh u la ong te ha ki, “Nga ruh ngan kylli ïa phi kawei ka jingkylli, to ïathuh te ha nga, te ngan sa ong ha phi da ka bor aïu ba nga leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis, ka long na bneng, lane na ki briew? to ïathuh ha nga.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïasaid hi paralok, ki da ong, “Lada ngin ong, ‘Na bneng’, un ong, ‘Hato balei te ba phim shym la ngeit ha u?’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, lada ngin ong, ‘Na ki briew’,” — ki la sheptieng ïa u paidbah; naba baroh ki ñiew ïa u Ïoannis kum u nongïathuhlypa uba da shisha.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki da ïathuh te, ki ong ha U Jisu, “Ngim tip.” Te U Jisu u da ïathuh, u ong ha ki, “Nga ruh ngam ong ha phi da ka bor aïu ba nga leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u la sdang ban kren ïa ki ha ki pharshi. “U briew u la thung ka brisoh, bad u la ker baroh sawdong, bad u la tih jaka tylliat soh Waiñ bad u la tei ïa ka ïing phira, bad u la ai wai ïa ka ha ki nongsumar bri, bad u la leit noh ruh sha kawei pat ka ri.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ha ka aïom babiang, u la phah ïa u shakri ha kita ki nongsumar bri, ba un ïoh diang na kita ki nongsumar bri na ki soh jong kata ka brisoh,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> hynrei, haba ki la kem ïa u, ki la sympat, bad ki la phah noh suda.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U la phah pat te sa uwei pat u shakri ha ki; ïa uta, ki la pynmong ïa ka khlieh jong u, bad ki la phah noh ïa u haba la pynjahburom.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la phah sa ïa uwei ruh: ïa uta, ki la pynïap noh; bad ïa bun kiwei pat; ïa kiwei ki la sympat, bad ïa kiwei pat ki la pynïap noh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u dang don sa uwei, u khun uba ieit eh jong u; u la phah ïa uta ruh uba khatduh ha ki, u da ong, ‘Kin burom ïa u khun jong nga.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, kita ki nongsumar bri ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, ‘Une u ban sa long u trai ka brisoh; ïa, ngin ïa-pynïap noh ïa u, te ka bynta kan long ka jong ngi’:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> haba ki la kem te ïa u, ki la ïa-pynïap noh, bad ki la ïabred noh shabar kata ka brisoh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, uta u trai ka brisoh un sa leh aïu? Un wan keiñ bad un pynjot noh ïa kita ki nongsumar bri, bad un sa ai ïa ka brisoh ha kiwei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Phim shym la pule te ïa kane Ka Jingthoh? “ ‘Uta u maw ïa uba ki nongtei ki la kyntait, ïa une la pynlong u khlieh ka dong:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> kane ka la long na U Trai, bad ka long kaba iphylla ha ki khmat jong ngi.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki la ïawad dong te ban kem ïa U; hynrei, ki la sheptieng ïa u paidbah; naba ki la tip ba U la kren ïa kata ka pharshi pyrshah ïa ki. Kumta, haba ki la iehnoh ïa U, ki la leit noh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki la phah te ha u kiba na ki Pharisi bad kiba na ki nongbud u Herod, ba kin riam ïa u ha kaba kren.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki te haba ki la wan, ki ong ha u, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi tip ba me long uba shisha bad ba mem ñiew ïano ïano ruh; naba mem khmih ïa ka khmat ki briew, hynrei, me hikai ïa ka lynti U Blei ha kaba shisha. Hato ka bit ne em ban ai khajna ha u Kaisar? ngin ai, ne ngim ai?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, u, ba u ithuh ïa ka buit arsap jong ki, u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi tynjuh ïa nga? wallam ha nga ka shi suka, ba ngan ïohi ïa ka.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki la wallam te ïa ka. U la ong te ha ki, “Ka jongno kane ka dur bad ka jingthoh shalor?” Ki te ki la ong ha u, “Ki jong u Kaisar.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Jisu u la ïathuh u la ong te ha ki, “To ai ha u Kaisar ïa kiei kiei ki jong u Kaisar, bad ha U Blei ïa kiei kiei ki jong U Blei.” Hangta ki la sngewkyndit shibun eh ïa u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Saddusi ki la wan ha u, kiba ong bymdon ka jingmihpat, bad ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ko Nonghikai, u Moses u la thoh ha ngi, ba lada un ïap noh u hynmen jongno jongno ruh, bad un iehnoh tnga, te ba um shym don khun, ba u para jong u un shim ïa ka tnga jong u, bad un pynmih symbai ïa la u hynmen.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> La don hynñiew ngut shipara; uba shuwa te u la ïoh tnga, bad haba u ïap um shym la iehnoh symbai:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> uba shi sien bud ruh u la shim ïa ka, u ruh u la ïap noh, bad um shym la iehnoh symbai: kumjuh ruh u ba-ar sien bud:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> kumta, kita ki hynñiew ngut ki la ïoh ïa ka bad kim shym la iehnoh symbai: ka bakhatduh eh na ki baroh, kata ka kynthei ruh ka la ïap noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata, ha ka jingmihpat haba kin mihpat, kan long ka tnga jongno na ki? naba kita ki hynñiew ngut ki la ïoh kurim ïa ka.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh u la ong te ha ki, “Ym dei namar kane ba phi bakla, ba phim tip ïa Ki Jingthoh, lymne ïa ka bor U Blei?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba haba kin mihpat na ki baïap, kim ïashongkurim, lymne pynshongkurim ïa ki, hynrei, ki long kum ki angel ha bneng.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, shaphang ki nongïap, ba yn pynmih pat ïa ki, phim ju pule ha Ka Kitab u Moses, kumno ba U Blei u la kren ha u ha kata ka 'law lynnong, u da ong. ‘Nga uba U Blei u Abraham, bad U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob ruh’?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Um long U Blei ki baïap, hynrei, U Blei ki ba-im: namar kata, phi bakla shikatdei eh.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Haba la wan te ha U, uwei na ki nongthoh uba la ïohsngew ba ki ïasaid paralok hi, uba da sngewthuh ruh ba U la ïathuh bha ïa ki, u la kylli ïa U, “Kano ka long ka hukum kaba kongsan na ki baroh?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Jisu u la ïathuh te ha u, “Kaba kongsan na ki hukum baroh long; ‘Sngew, A Israel, U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi u long uwei U Trai:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> men ieit ruh ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me da ka dohnud jong me baroh, bad da ka mynsiem jong me baroh, bad da ka jingmut jong me baroh, bad da ka bor jong me baroh: kane keiñ ka hukum ka bakongsan’:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ka ba-ar ruh ka long kane: ‘Men ieit ïa la u paramarjan kumba ïa lade.’ Ym don ka hukum kawei pat kaba kham khraw ïa kine.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Uta u nongthoh u la ong te ha U, “Kaba dei, ko Nonghikai! me la ong kaba shisha, ba u long uwei, bad ym don uwei pat, hynrei, tang ma u:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad ban ieit ïa u da ka dohnud baroh, bad da ka jingmut baroh, bad da ka mynsiem baroh, bad da ka bor baroh, bad ban ieit ïa la u paramarjan kumba ïa lade, ka long kham kor ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ïa ki jingkñia baroh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda U Jisu u la ïohi te ba u la ïathuh stad, U la ong ha u, “Mem long jngai na ka hima U Blei.” Te naduh kata, ym don ba nud ban kylli ei ei ïa U.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Jisu u la ïathuh u la ong ruh, haba u dang hikai ha ka templ, “Kumno ba ki nongthoh ki ong ba U Khrist u long u khun u Dabid?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> naba u Dabid hi u kren da U Mynsiem Bakhuid: “ ‘U Trai u la ong ïa U Trai jong nga, To shong ma me ha ka kti kamon jong nga, tad ynda ngan pynlong ïa kiba shun ïa me, ka jingïuh hapoh ki kjat jong me.’",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “U Dabid hi u khot ‘U Trai’ ïa u; nangno te u long u khun jong u?” Te bun u paidbah u la sngew ïa u da kaba sngewbha.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U la ong te ha ki ha ka jinghikai jong u: “To kiar na kita ki nongthoh, kiba kwah ban ïaid kai ha ki jaiñkup bajynsur, bad ïa ki jingnguh ha ki ïew,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad ïa ki jingshong bakor tam ha ki synagog, bad ïa ki jaka kiba kham donburom ha ki jingkhawai;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> kiba bam duh ïa ki ïing ki riewkynthei, bad kiba duwai jlan ruh khnang ban tyllep; kine kin ïoh diang ka jingpynrem kaba kham khraw.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te U Jisu haba u la shong ha marpyrshah ka jingkynshew, u la khmih kumno ba u paidbah u noh sbai sha kata ka jingkynshew: bad bun ki bariewspah ki la noh shikatdei.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Haba la wan te kawei ka riewkynthei ka baduk, ka la noh ar damli, kiba long la jan shi peisa.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Haba u la khot ha u ïa ki synran jong u, u la ong ha ki, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kane ka riewkynthei ka baduk ka la noh kham bun ïa kita baroh kiba la noh sha kata ka jingkynshew;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> naba kita baroh, ki la noh na kaba sah tam ïa ki, hynrei, kane, na ka jingkyrduh jong ka, ka la noh baroh katba ka don, wat ïa ka jingim jong ka phar.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te katba U dang mih noh na ka templ, uwei na ki synran jong U, u ong ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, ha khmih, ki maw kat kine bad ki jingtei kat kine!”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh te U la ong ha u, “Me ïohi ïa kine ki jingtei bakhraw? yn ym iehnoh maw halor u maw, u ban ym pynhap noh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te katba u dang shong ha u lum ki Olib ha marpyrshah ka templ, u Petros bad u Jakob bad u Ïoannis bad u Andriw, ki la kylli jar jar ïa u,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “To ïathuh ha ngi, lano kine kiei kiei ruh kin long? bad ka dak kaba kumno ha ban sa pyndep ïa kine kiei kiei baroh?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Jisu u la sdang ban ong ha ki, “To sumar ïoh ba uno uno ruh un shukor ïa phi:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> naba bun kin wan ha ka kyrteng jong nga, ki da ong, ‘Ma nga U Khrist’, bad kin shukor ïa shibun.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, haba phin ïohsngew shaphang ki thma bad ïa ki jingbna ki thma, wat khuslai phi; naba ka dei ba kine kin long, hynrei, ka bakut kam pat long.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba ka kynja bynriew kan ïeng ïaleh bad ka kynja bynriew, ka hima ruh bad ka hima; bad ki jingkhynñiuh jumai kin long ha bun ki jaka, bad kin long ki 'nemsniew: kine ki jingsdang ki jingjynjar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Hynrei, to sumar ïa lade; naba kin ai noh ïa phi ha ki jingbishar, bad ha ki synagog yn sympat ïa phi, bad yn pynïeng ïa phi ha khmat ki lyngskor bad ki syiem na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka dei shuwa ba yn ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki kynja bynriew baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ynda kin ïalam ïa phi bad kin ai noh ïa phi, wat sngewkhuslai lypa phi kaei ba phin kren, lymne wat puson lypa; hynrei, kaei kaei ruh ba yn ai ha phi ha kata ka por, ïa kata phin kren, naba phi phim long kiba kren, hynrei, U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U para te un ai noh ïa u para sha ka ban ïap, bad u kpa ruh ïa la u khun, bad ki khun kin ïeng ïaleh ïa ki kmie ki kpa, bad kin pynïap ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki briew baroh kin shun ïa phi na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga; hynrei, jar u ban da ïaineh ha ban da kut, uta keiñ, u ban lait im.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Hynrei, ynda phin ïohi ïa kata ka jingijli bapynduh, kaba la kren da u Daniel u nongïathuhlypa, ba ka ïeng sha ka bymdei (Jar uba pule un da sngap,) ynda kumta, kita kiba ha Judia, to kin ïaphet ïap noh sha ki lum;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> jar uba halor ïing ruh, wat ai un hiar hapoh ka ïing, lymne rung shapoh ban shim ei ei na ka ïing jong u;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad jar uba don ha lyngkha, wat ai un wan kylla dien pat, ban shim ïa ka jaiñkup jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, kordit ïa kita kiba punkhun, bad ïa kita kiba ai buiñ ha kita ki sngi!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, to duwai ba kata kan ym long myntlang,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> naba kin long ki sngi ki jingjynjar, kat ki bym pat ju la long la myndanglong ka pyrthei ïa kaba U Blei u la thaw, haduh mynta, kat kita ruh kin ym long shuh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te lymda u la pynduna U Trai ïa kita ki sngi, kan ym da lait im kawei ka doh; hynrei, na ka bynta kiba la jied ïa kiba u la jied, u la pynduna ïa kita ki sngi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, lada uno uno ruh un ong ha phi, ‘Ha khmih, hangne U Khrist’, lane, ‘Ha khmih, hangta’, phi wat ngeit;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> naba ki Khrist lamler bad ki nongïathuhlypa lamler kin mih, bad kin pyni ki dak bad ki jingphylla ïa ka ban shukor noh, lada lah, wat ïa kiba la jied.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, to sumar phi! ha khmih, nga la ïathuhlypa ha phi ïa kiei kiei baroh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Hynrei, ha kita ki sngi, hadien kata ka jingjynjar, ïa ka sngi yn pyndum, bad u bnai un ym ai la ka jingshai,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad ki khlur bneng kin hap noh, bad ïa ki bor kiba ha ki bneng yn pynkhynñiuh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, kin ïohi ïa U Khun u briew ba u da wan ha ki lyoh, bad ka borbah bad ka burom ruh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta ruh, un phah ïa ki angel, bad un ïalum lang ïa kiba la jied jong u na ki saw lyer, naduh ka bakut ka pyrthei haduh ka bakut ka bneng.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “To nang te ïa ka pharshi jong u dieng Dumbur. Mynba u tnat jong u, u la dang khie lung bad ba u sei sla, phi tip ba ka lyiur ka la jan;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> kumjuh ruh ma phi, ynda phin ïohi ba jia kine kiei kiei ruh, phin tip ba u la jan, ha ka jingkhang keiñ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kane ka pateng bynriew kan ym leit noh, tad ynda la leh ïa kine kiei kiei baroh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ka bneng bad ka khyndew te kin duh noh, hynrei, ki ktien jong nga kin ym duh noh satia.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Hynrei, shaphang kata ka sngi bad kata ka por ruh ym don ba tip, em, wat ki angel kiba ha bneng, lymne U Khun, hynrei, tang U Kpa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> To sumar, to sharai, to duwai ruh; naba phim tip lano ka long kata ka sngi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Namar U Khun u briew, u long kum u briew uba leit jingleit sha kawei pat ka ri; uba la iehnoh ïa la ka ïing, bad uba la ai ha la ki shakri ka bor, ha uwei uwei ruh ka kam la ka jong ka jong, bad uba la hukum ruh ïa u nongap jingkhang ban sharai.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Namar kata, to sharai, naba phim tip lano uta u trai ka ïing u wan, ha kaba la janmiet, ne shiteng synñia, ne haba riew syiar, ne mynstep;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ïoh, haba u wan kyndit, un shem ïa phi ba dang thiah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ïa kaba nga ong te ha phi, nga ong ha baroh: To sharai.”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda la ar sngi te la long Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, bad Ki Kpu Khlem Thiat; ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh te ki la wad dong kumno kin ïoh kem tuh ïa u, ba kin pynïap ruh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, ki la ong, “Ym ha Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ïoh ba ka jingkhihwin ki briew kan long.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Haba U dang don te ha Bethania, ha ïing u Simon u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh, katba U shong bam, ka kynthei ka la wan kaba don ka dabi alabaster kaba dap da ka jingsleh basngur, ka bakordor eh; te haba ka la plie ïa kata ka dabi alabaster, ka la theh ruh ha ka khlieh jong U.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, don kiba la sngewbitar ha lade, ki da ong, “Ïa ka ban lei la pynlehnohei ïa kata ka jingsleh?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> naba ïa kane ka jingsleh lah ban die laispah suka tam, bad ban ai ha ki baduk.” Ki la ïakhñium ruh ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong, “To iehnoh ïa ka; balei phi pynkhuslai ïa ka? ka la leh ka kam babha ïa nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar phi don ki baduk lem bad phi ha la ka sngi, bad ynda phi mon phi lah ban leh bha ïa ki; hynrei, ïa nga phim ïoh keiñ ha la ka sngi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kane katba ka lah ka la leh, ka la thew lypa ban pynsleh ïa ka met jong nga ïa ka ban tep.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba shano shano ruh sha kaba yn ïalap ïa kane ka gospel ha ka pyrthei baroh satlak, yn ïathuh ruh ïa kaba kane ka la leh, ïa ka ban kynmaw ïa ka.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Judas Iskariot te, uwei na ki khat-ar ngut, u la leit noh ha ki rangbah lyngdoh, ba un ïoh aiti noh ïa U ha ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew, ki la ïakmen, bad ki la ïakular ban ai tyngka ha u; u te u la wad kumno un ïoh lad kaba bit ban ai noh ïa U.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ka sngi nyngkong Ki Kpu Khlem Thiat, ha kaba ki ju kñia ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ki synran jong u ki ong ha u, “Hangno me mon ba ngin leit khreh, ba men ïoh bam ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u la phah ar ngut na ki synran jong u, bad u ong ha ki, “Khie leit shapoh kato ka shnong, te u briew uba bah shi kum  ka um, un ïakynduh bad phi; to bud ïa u,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> te shaei shaei ba un leit rung, ong ha u trai ïing, ‘U Nonghikai u ong, “Hangno kata ka kamra jong nga, ha kaba ngan ïoh bam ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait lem bad ki synran jong nga?” ’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u hi un pyni ha phi ïa ka kamra haneng kaba khraw, ïa kaba la siang jingbuh lypa; hangta phin ïakhreh ïa ngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, ki synran jong u ki la leit noh, bad ki la wan shapoh kata ka shnong, bad ki la shem kumba u la ong ha ki; bad ki la ïakhreh ïa kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba la janmiet te, u wan bad kita ki khat-ar ngut.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Haba ki dang ïashong bam, bad ba ki ïabam ruh, U Jisu u la ong, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba uwei na phi uba bam lem bad nga, un die noh ïa nga.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la sdang te ban sngewsih, bad ban ïa-ong ïa u, uwei pa uwei, “Dei ma nga?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “U dei uwei na ki khat-ar, uta keiñ, uba ïawieh lem bad nga ha ka pliang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Khun u briew shisha un sa leit, kumba la thoh shaphang jong u, hynrei, kordit ïa uta u briew da uba yn die noh ïa U Khun u briew! Ka la bha ïa uta u briew lada ym shym la kha satia ïa u!”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Haba ki dang ïabam ruh, U Jisu u la shim ïa u kpu, bad haba u la lah nguh u la kdiah, bad u la ai ha ki, bad u la ong, “To shim, to bam, une u long ka met jong nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba u la shim ïa ka khuri ruh, bad haba u la lah nguh, u la ai ha ki; ki ruh ki la dih baroh na ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Kane ka long ka snam jong nga ka jong ka jutang ka bathymmai, ïa ka ban sa pynmih noh na ka bynta kiba bun;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> shisha nga ong ha phi, ba ngan ym dih shuh na une u soh u dieng Waiñ, tad ynda kata ka sngi haba nga dih thymmai ïa ka ha ka hima U Blei.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba ki la ïarwai, ki la leit noh sha u lum ki Olib.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad U Jisu u ong ha ki, “Phi baroh phin thut namar jong nga, naba la thoh: ‘Ngan shoh ïa u nongsharai, bad yn pynsaphred ïa ki langbrot.’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, ynda la pynmih pat ïa nga, ngan leit sha shuwa jong phi sha Galilaïa.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong ha U, “Lada baroh ruh kin thut, hynrei, nga, em.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Jisu u ong te ha u, “Shisha nga ong ha me, ba wat ma me ha kane ka sngi, ha kane hi ka miet keiñ, haba um pat riew u syiar ar sien, men len ïa nga lai sien.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, u la kren kynsan kham tam, “Lada ka dei ïa nga ban ïap lem bad me, ngan ym len satia ïa me.” Kumjuh ruh de ki la ong baroh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki la wan ruh sha ka jaka kaba kyrteng “Gethsemane”; u ong te ha ki synran jong u, “To ïashong hangne, katba nga nang duwai.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u la shim lem bad u ïa u Petros bad ïa u Jakob bad ïa u Ïoannis; bad u la sdang ban sngewshyrkhei eh, bad ban sngewkordit eh ruh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ka mynsiem jong nga ka pisa eh, kum ban sa ïap; to ïaishong hangne, to ïa-ap ruh.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba u la leit sha shuwa khyndiat, u la dem ha khyndew, bad u la duwai, ba lada don lad, ba kata ka por kan leit noh na u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U la ong ruh, “Abba, ko Kpa, kiei kiei baroh ki long kiba lah ha me; to pynphai noh ïa kane ka khuri na nga; pynban, ym ïa kaba nga mon, hynrei, ïa kaba me mon.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U wan te bad u shem ïa ki ba ki da ïohthiah; bad u ong ha u Petros. “Ko Simon, me ïohthiah? mem lah ban ap shi por?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> To ïasharai, to ïaduwai ruh, ïoh ba phin leit bsut hapoh ka jingpynshoi; ka mynsiem shisha ka kloi, hynrei, ka doh ka tlot.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Haba u la leit noh pat te, u la duwai u da ong ïa kijuh ki ktien.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Haba u la wan phai pat ruh, u la shem ïa ki, ba ki da ïohthiah pat, naba ki khmat jong ki, ki la khia; te kim tip kaei ba kin ïathuh ha u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> U la wan ruh ka balai sien, bad u ong ha ki, “Phi nang thiah mynta? phi nang jahthait ruh? keiñ noh! la jia ka por, ha khmih, la die noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki nongpop.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> To ïeng, ngin ïaleit noh, ha khmih, uta uba die noh ïa nga u la jan.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, katba U dang kren, u Judas u wan, uba long uwei na ki khat-ar ngut, lem bad u ruh don u paidbah babun bad ki waitlam bad ki diengduh, na ki rangbah lyngdoh bad na ki nongthoh bad na ki tymmen basan de.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te uta uba la die noh ïa U, u la lah ai ka dak ïakut bad ki, u da ong, “Ïa uba ngan doh, U dei uta; to phin kem ïa U, bad ïalam noh skhem.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te ynda u la wan, kumne kumne ruh, u la leit ha U, u ong, “Ko Kynrad, Kynrad”; u la doh ruh ïa U.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ki te ki la buh ïa la ki kti ha U, bad ki la kem ïa U.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Uwei te na kita kiba ïeng hajan, haba u la sei la ka waitlam, u la pom ïa u shakri u rangbah lyngdoh, bad u la mait noh ïa ka shkor jong u.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh, u la ong te ha ki, “Kumba ha u nongtuh, phi la mih noh, bad ki waitlam bad ki diengduh ruh, ban ïakem ïa nga?",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Nga la ju don ha la ka sngi bad phi ha ka templ, nga da hikai, te phim shym la kem ïa nga. Hynrei, ïa Ki Jingthoh, donkam ba yn pyndep.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te baroh ki la iehnoh ïa u bad ki la phet ïap noh.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Hynrei, don uwei u samla uba la bud ïa U, uba kup ïa ka jaiñ linen bani halor ka met lyngkhuit jong u bad ki la kem ïa u ruh;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> te u la iehnoh ïa kata ka jaiñkup bani, bad u la phet ïap noh lyngkhuit na ki.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Te ki la ïalam noh ïa U Jisu ha uta u rangbah lyngdoh, bad kita ki rangbah lyngdoh baroh, bad kita ki tymmen basan bad kita ki nongthoh de ki la ïawan lang lem bad u.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> U Petros te u la bud ïa U na sha jngai haduh hapoh phyllaw jong uta u rangbah lyngdoh bad u la shong lem bad kita ki shakri, u da syaid ding ruh.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kata ka dorbar baroh ki la ïawad ka sakhi pyrshah ïa U Jisu, ïa ka ban pynïap ïa U; te kim shem,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> naba bun ki la ïasakhi lamler ïa U, hynrei, kita ki jingsakhi kim ïadei satia.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Te don kiba la ïeng joit bad ki la sakhi lamler pyrshah ïa U, ki da ong,",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> “Ngi la ïohsngew ïa u ba u da ong, ‘Ngan pynjot ïa kane ka templ ba la thaw da ki kti, bad ngan tei lai sngi ïa kawei pat ka bym da ki kti.’ ”",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> La kumta ruh, ka jingsakhi jong ki kam ïabeit satia.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Uta u rangbah lyngdoh te haba u la ïeng joit hapdeng, u la kylli ïa U Jisu, u da ong, “Mem ïathuh ei ei ruh? Ka long aïu ba kine ki ïasakhi pyrshah ïa me?”",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> U te U la shu sngap, bad um ïathuh ei ei ruh em. Uta u rangbah lyngdoh u la kylli pat ïa U, bad u ong ha U, “Me long uta U Khrist, U Khun jong Uba la kyrkhu?”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> U Jisu te u la ong, “Nga long. Bad phin ïohi ïa U Khun u briew ba u da shong sha ka kti kamon jong ka Bor, bad ba u da wan ha ki lyoh bneng.”",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Te u rangbah lyngdoh u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u ong, “Ngi dang donkam aïu pat ïa ki sakhi?",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Phi la ïohsngew ïa kata ka jingkrenbeiñ blei; phi mut kumno?” Ki baroh te ki la pynrem ïa U, ba U dei ban ïap;",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> don kiba la sdang te ban bynthiew ïa U, bad ban tap matlah ïa ki khmat jong U, bad ban shoh ïa U, bad ban ong ruh ha U, “To ïathuh antad”: kita ki shakri ruh ki la thab ïa U da ki slakti.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Te haba u Petros u dang don harum ha kata ka phyllaw, kawei na kita ki shakri jong u rangbah lyngdoh ka la wan;",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> haba ka la ïohi te ïa u Petros ba u da syaid ding, ka la khmih ïa u, bad ka ong, “Me ruh me la long lem bad U Jisu u nong Nasaret.”",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> Hynrei u la len, u da ong, “Ngam tip, lymne ngam shemphang kaei ba pha ong.” Bad u la mih noh shabar sha ka baranda; te u syiar u la riew.",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> Haba kata ka shakri te ka la ïohi ïa u pat, ka la sdang ban ong ha kita kiba ïeng hajan, “Uto u long uwei na ki.”",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> Hynrei, u la len pat. Ynda la shibit te kita kiba ïeng hajan ki la ong pat ha u Petros, “Shisha me long uwei na ki; naba me long u nong Galilaïa.”",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> Hynrei, u la sdang ban tim ban smai ruh, “Ngam ithuh ïa une u briew uba phi kren shaphang jong u.”",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, uta u syiar u la riew ar wat. Te u Petros u la kynmaw ïa kata ka ktien kaba U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Mynshuwa ba un riew u syiar ar sien, men len ïa nga lai sien.” Haba u la puson ruh ïa kata, u la lynñiar."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, ynda ka la shai, kita ki rangbah lyngdoh ki la ïasylla bad kita ki tymmen basan bad kita ki nongthoh bad kata ka dorbar baroh ruh; haba ki la khum ïa U Jisu, ki la ïalam noh ïa u, bad ki la ai noh ha u Pilat.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Pilat u la kylli ïa U, “Me long U Syiem ki Jiw?” U te U da ïathuh U la ong ha u, “Me ong.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki rangbah lyngdoh ki la mudui ïa u shaphang bun kiei kiei ruh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Pilat te u la kylli pat ïa U, u da ong, “Mem ïathuh ei ei? Ha khmih katno kiei kiei ba ki mudui ïa me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu um shym ïathuh ei ei shuh, kat ban pynlyngngoh ïa u Pilat.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Jinglait, u ju pyllait ha ki, ïa uwei u nongsah byndi, kat uba ki la ïapan na u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te la don uwei uba ki khot “u Barabbas”, ïa uba la khum lem bad kita kiba la pynkhihwin, ki briew kiba la pynïap briew ha ka jingkhihwin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U paidbah te haba u la pyrta jam, u la sdang ban pan, ba un leh kumba u ju leh ha ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Pilat u la ïathuh ha ki, u da ong, “Phi mon ba ngan pyllait noh ha phi ïa U Syiem jong ki Jiw?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba u la tip ba namar kaba bishni kita ki rangbah lyngdoh ki la ai noh ïa U.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, kita ki rangbah lyngdoh ki la pynkhih ïa uta u paidbah, ba un pyllait noh keiñ ïa u Barabbas ha ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pilat u da ïathuh u la ong pat ha ki, “Namar kata, phi mon ba ngan leh aïu ïa uta uba phi khot ‘u Syiem ki Jiw’?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki te ki la ïapyrta jam pat, “Sahnarphna ïa u.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Pilat te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Balei, u la leh ka bymman aïu?” Ki te ki la ïapyrta jam kham tam, “Sahnarphna ïa u.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u Pilat, ba u da mon ban pynsngewbha ïa uta u paidbah, u la pyllait noh ha ki ïa u Barabbas; te u la ai noh ïa U Jisu, ynda u la sympat ïa U, ban sahnarphna.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki shipai te ki la ïalam noh ïa u hapoh phyllaw, kaba long ka ïingbah u lyngskor, bad ki ïakhot lang baroh shi kynhun;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ki la pynkup ïa u da ka jaiñ saw bthuh, bad haba ki la ïathain ïa ka pansngiat shiah, ki la pynphong ha u,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la sdang ban nguh ïa u, “Khublei U Syiem ki Jiw!”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la shoh ruh ïa ka khlieh jong u da u prew, bad ki la bynthiew ïa u, bad haba ki la dem la ki khohsiew, ki la mane ïa u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda ki la lah pyrthuhbeiñ te ïa u, ki la loit noh ïa kata ka jaiñ saw bthuh na u, bad ki la pynkup ïa u la ki jong ki jaiñ, bad ki la ïalam noh ïa u ban sahnarphna ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki la pynbor te ïa uwei u Simon u nong Kyrini, uba ïaid lait, haba u wan na ka ri bri (u kpa u Alexander bad u Ruphos), ban bah ïa ka diengphna jong U.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki la ïalam ruh ïa U ha ka jaka Golgotha, kaba long, haba la batai, “Ka jaka maloi khlieh”.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki la ai ha U ka umsoh Waiñ kaba la ïakhleh bad ka mirr ban dih; hynrei, um shim satia.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ki la sahnarphna ïa U, ki ïabynta ïa ki jaiñ jong U, ba ki da ïakhalai ïa ki, kaei ba uwei uwei un shim.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ka la lai baje haba ki la sahnarphna ïa U.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad la don ka jingthoh shalor shaphang ka pop jong U kaba la thoh haneng, “U Syiem ki Jiw.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki la sahnarphna ïa ar ngut ki dakaid ruh lem bad U, uwei sha kamon, uwei sha kadiang jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, la pyndep ïa kata Ka Jingthoh, kaba ong: “La ñiew ïa u lem bad ki nongpalat.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kiba ïaid shata te ki la krenbeiñ ïa U, ki da kyrngah ki khlieh jong ki, ki da ong ruh, “A, me uba pynduh ïa ka templ, bad uba tei ïa ka, lai sngi!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> To pynim ïa lade, to hiar noh ruh na kato ka diengphna.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumjuh ruh kita ki rangbah lyngdoh haba ki krenbeiñ, ki la ong paralok hi lem bad kita ki nongthoh, “U la pynim ïa kiwei, ïa lade pleng um lah ban pynim!",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To U Khrist, uba U Syiem ki Israel, un hiar noh mynta na kato ka diengphna, ba ngin ïohi, bad ngin ïoh ngeit ruh!” Kita ruh ïa kiba la sahnarphna lem bad U, ki la krenbeiñ ïa U.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ynda la dap hynriew baje, ka la long dum ha kata ka ri baroh, haduh kaba khyndai baje.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te hamar kaba khyndai baje U Jisu u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, u da ong, “Eloi Eloi lamma sabakhthani?” (kaba long, haba la batai, “U Blei jong nga, U Blei jong nga balei me la iehnoh ïa nga?”)",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kiba na kita te kiba ïeng hajan, haba ki la ïohsngew, ki la ong, “Ha sngap, u khot ïa u Elias.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Uwei te haba u la mareh u la pyndap ïa ka spanj da ka bajew, bad u la spaiñ de ha u dieng, u la pyndih ïa U, u da ong, “To ieh phi, ngin ïakhmih la u wan u Elias ban pynhiar noh ïa u.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Haba U Jisu u la pynmih noh te ïa ka ktien bajam, u la ai noh ïa ka mynsiem.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te ka jingkah ka jong ka templ ka la kad ar liang, naduh jrong haduh tbian.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U rangbah shispah te uba ïeng hajan ha pyrshah jong U, haba u ïohi ba kumta U ai noh la ka mynsiem, u la ong, “Shisha une u briew u la long U Khun U Blei.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> La don ruh ki kynthei de kiba jngoh na sha jngai, hapdeng jong ki la don ka Mari ka nong Magdala, bad ka Mari ka kmie u Jakob uba rit bad u Ïosis, bad ka Salomi;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> kine ruh, mynba u don ha Galilaïa, ki la ju bud ïa u, bad ki ju shakri ïa u; bad bun kiwei kiwei ruh ki kynthei kiba la kiew lem bad u sha Jerusalem.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Mynta te haba la janmiet, namar ba ka long ka sngi Pynkhreh (kaba long ha shuwa ka Sabbaton),",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> haba la wan u Joseph uba na Arimathaïa, u myntri uba donburom, uba u hi ruh u ju ap kyrmen ïa ka hima U Blei, da kaba shlur u la leit hapoh ha u Pilat, bad u la pan ïa ka met U Jisu.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te u Pilat u la sngewkyndit ba U la da ïap katta; te haba u la khot ha u ïa uta u rangbah shispah, u kylli ïa u, la U la lah ïap kham slem.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Haba u la ïoh tip te na uta u rangbah shispah, u la ai sngewbha ïa ka met ha u Joseph.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te u la thied ïa ka jaiñ linen bani, bad haba u la pynhiar noh ïa U, u la sop spaiñ ïa U ha kata ka jaiñ linen, bad u la buh ïa U ha ka jingtep, ïa kaba la shna ha u mawsiang, bad u la pyntyllun ïa u maw ha ka jingkhang kata ka jingtep.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te ka Mari ka nong Magdala bad ka Mari ka kmie u Ïosis, ki la ïakhmih hangno ba la buh ïa U."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda la lah ka Sabbaton, te ka Mari ka nong Magdala, bad ka Mari ka kmie u Jakob, bad ka Salomi, ki la thied ïa ki jingiwbih, ba kin ïoh wan ban pynsleh ïa U.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te dang step eh ha ka sngi nyngkong jong ka taïew, ki la ïawan sha kata ka jingtep, hamar kaba mih ka sngi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki la ïakren paralok hi te, “Uei u ban pyntyllun noh ïa u maw ïa ngi na ka jingkhang ka jingtep?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> (Te haba ki la jngoh, ki la ïohi ba la lah pyntyllun noh ïa uta u maw); naba u la long uba khraw eh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba ki la bsut te ha kata ka jingtep, ki la ïohi ïa u samla uba shong sha kamon, uba la kup ïa ka jaiñ lieh kaba jynsur; ki la sheptieng ruh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Wat sheptieng; phi wad ïa U Jisu uba na Nasaret, ïa uba la sahnarphna? U la mihpat, um don hangne: ha khmih ka jaka ha kaba ki la ïabuh ïa U.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, khie leit ïathuh ha ki synran jong U, bad ha u Petros, ba U leit sha shuwa jong phi sha Galilaïa; hangta phin ïohi ïa U, kumba U la ong ha phi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Haba ki la mih noh te, ki la phet noh na kata ka jingtep, namar kaba sngewphieng bad kaba sngewkyndit ki la ngat ha ki; hynrei, kim shym la ïathuh ei ei ruh hano hano ruh naba ki la sheptieng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haba U la mihpat te mynstep eh ha ka sngi nyngkong jong ka taïew, U la paw nyngkong ha ka Mari ka nong Magdala, na kaba U la lah beh noh ïa ki hynñiew ki ksuid.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka te ka la leit ïathuh ha kita kiba la ju don lem bad U, katba ki dang ïasngewsih bad ïaïam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki te haba ki la ïohsngew ba U dang im, bad ba la lah ïohi ruh ïa U da ka, kim ngeit.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hadien kata, U la paw ha kawei pat ka dur ha ki ar ngut na ki katba ki ïa-ïaid ha la ka lynti sha ka ri bri.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki ruh ki la leit noh bad ki la ïathuh ha kita kiba dang sah, hynrei, ïa ki ruh, kim ngeit.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hadien te U la paw ha kita ki khatwei ngut hi, katba ki ïashong bam lem; bad U la pynrem ïa ka jingbymngeit bad ïa ka jingeh ka dohnud jong ki, namar ba kim ngeit ïa kita kiba la lah ïohi ïa U hadien ba U la mihpat.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “To leit sha ka pyrthei baroh, bad to ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki bynriew baroh;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> te uta uba ngeit bad ïoh pynbaptis, yn pynim; hynrei, ïa uta u bymngeit, yn pynrem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kine ki dak ruh kin bud ïa kita kiba ngeit; ha ka kyrteng jong nga kin ïabeh noh ïa ki ksuid, kin kren da ki thylliej bathymmai;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kin rah noh ïa ki bseiñ, bad lada kin dih ei ei ruh kaba pynïap, kan ym pynsniew ïa ki keiñ; kin buh ïa ki kti ha ki bapang, bad kita kin khiah.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta te ïa U Trai Jisu, hadien ba U la lah kren ha ki, la pdiang soit sha bneng, bad U la shong sha kamon U Blei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki te haba ki la mih noh, ki la ïalap kylleng sawdong, U Trai ruh U da trei lem, bad U da pynskhem ïa kata ka ktien da ki dak kiba bud. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;